["addation_ea6f3974f8d92ea1"] = "If you can get through this quietly, you should be able to just melt away with the crowd.", 
["addation_c8ee156eb4d7d774"] = "I don\'t even wanna know what you guys are up to this time. Just give me the coordinates.", 
["addation_7b1d833aa318e84f"] = "We got a bank here. Not a big branch but I\'ve learned the vault is temporarily holding stacks of cash in transit. Foreign exchange notes. Anyway, you know how to do it - your way. Sneak in silent, or unleash hell. Either way, I got a little idea for how to lift the money out of there. You\'ll see what I mean. I think you\'ll like it.", 
