["addation_2be6628e84ed0cfa"] = "What the fuck did that tree do to you? Huh?", 
["addation_93c759bb3d9562cf"] = "Get inside the truck! The chopper is going to airlift the whole damn thing out!", 
["addation_0362859b1bbf4027"] = "There are bandit barriers in the bank - you can close \'em from the security office. Will help keep cops out of your area of operation.", 
["addation_3e26569cf1104ec9"] = "Thank you for preserving our way of life. Money is coming your way like a ten million gallon oil spill.", 
["addation_f78550f179a206fe"] = "Bile is on the way with the chopper.", 
["addation_d73ca819d6195d5c"] = "I\'m sorry. No. I don\'t think the pigs would appreciate that. Even if they\'re dead.", 
["addation_5e1feb701da14c74"] = "Alright I\'m here. Get in quick so we can get out of here.", 
["addation_051a379b09eef3a1"] = "Gotta be a power box that controls the barriers. Find it!", 
["addation_b508805d26f05597"] = "The magnet is in place. Time to pull it out of here.", 
["addation_2f081ade1898312f"] = "The code should have a zero at the beginning.", 
["addation_2b5a1b26f63d4481"] = "Alright, I\'m here to do some heavy lifting!", 
["addation_18bd6fcbf017bdec"] = "Make space for the escape van - get those police cars out of the way!", 
["addation_c7b2db65ecd992b7"] = "You still have 16 left!", 
["addation_02b64b336a1e55f7"] = "Bring those trees down!", 
["addation_49d17a70eb4a1ffb"] = "Great, you found some evidence! Analyze it in the lab. Let\'s see if there\'s any trace of the traitor\'s DNA on it.", 
["addation_0bd1f32c62ea4bd7"] = "Let someone else handle that shit. I want Yuri.", 
["addation_3344d3d3d08275fd"] = "Gonna give you a motherfucking faceful of lead!", 
["addation_c9620f314a91f942"] = "Don\'t mind him, he\'s just hitchin\' a ride.", 
["addation_78941eb4981a66ee"] = "What the hell, I\'ll do you guys a favor...", 
["addation_57cd1fa498ce408b"] = "You don\'t wanna go back to prison, right?", 
["addation_c6f075340b168440"] = "Cut that fence and get down to the hangars. The Mendozas are in there.", 
["addation_55e59a7a3773db4b"] = "The vault is just beyond here. You got that code?", 
["addation_ae567c8193619031"] = "We\'re running low on spending money, so if you find anything else worth taking...", 
["addation_47ba0b4021a1c13d"] = "It\'s somewhere close. I wanna see the funds. ", 
["addation_5651423588381ca5"] = "That\'s the hatch! I\'ve got an idea for it. Bile is going to be Santa, and since you\'re such good boys and girls...", 
["addation_15693b39fee4e339"] = "You knocked him out? Really?", 
["addation_e429441819b38f1f"] = "Chopper\'s headed out, but stay cool - it\'ll be back. Look for more loot in the forest. And stay safe.", 
["addation_8443dd6f97f3079d"] = "Remember guys, we need seven bags to escape.", 
["addation_bde5f21315526d36"] = "Okay, think the bridge is looking good for a drop point.", 
["addation_3297617776768e37"] = "The evidence that Hoxton spoke of will be in that lock-up. Look for it. It should be marked out.", 
["addation_6e59d31b0aea9e3e"] = "Nice! 20!", 
["addation_02c9c113d0268bae"] = "I count... two guys.", 
["addation_06183aaf10c61d34"] = "There\'s one there. ", 
["addation_492842c72d31224a"] = "Let\'s get this taken care of. I got somewhere to be.", 
["addation_54fddf53416d55a4"] = "They\'re on the street...", 
["addation_b0cf9f825e521504"] = "Dammit! The plane snagged the cage but there was no goddamn cash. You guys need to pick it up and haul it out.", 
["addation_e0e6372071f145d6"] = "Come on. Climb aboard! Well fucking done, my friends!", 
["addation_19556e28199b5338"] = "Not sure they\'re the same as the others.", 
["addation_c355dd19804806e0"] = "Boat\'s ready for you.        ", 
["addation_1bbd07f04a908034"] = "These fuckers are trying to rip us off!", 
["addation_3fe63b7dd786f49d"] = "Turn the valve and unleash the cash. Banks up.", 
["addation_fc9402e007aeafdb"] = "Great. Now get it to the vault. We\'re doing this the old fashioned way.", 
["addation_22eb8a5ce7cce2c3"] = "Right, now let me just get this sorted. Won\'t be a jiffy.", 
["addation_788d747a12aaec28"] = "Okay, same as before: secure as many bags as you can or leave this place. Make up your mind!", 
["addation_08c0ef5d39cbff50"] = "Right, follow me and we\'ll get you out. Hope you got what you wanted.", 
["addation_f444545c7469f09f"] = "That\'s ten!", 
["addation_fdb4e8f0d04c33aa"] = "I have been running guns in the Caribbean for a while. It\'s been very profitable, but some of the old movers in the region don\'t approve of my presence on the local market. The Bolivian Sosa Cartel specifically. As they could not compete with me on level terms, they decided to attack my operation - sinking one of my ships, stealing my merchandise and killing my operatives. That was very unwise. Now they must pay. You will collect that payment, in blood.", 
["addation_94b61280405d6294"] = "That was messy but sometimes, it gets messy. But you ended up on top. That\'s what\'s important. Great work!", 
["addation_23c7eb08fba5d33b"] = "Second truck opened! Check it!", 
["addation_e5f27c858d053387"] = "Hook the winches up to the floor!", 
["addation_d4ed42d2ef62bcf3"] = "All of you need to be inside the dealership so I can blow up the C4!", 
["addation_0f09e0d788eebca9"] = "Are you lost? Jump out of window. Way out is straight down.", 
["addation_9536d4175ed29edb"] = "Go! Go! You gotta meet up with the driver!", 
["addation_f7c4134e0194621f"] = "And... yes, that is a satisfactory piece of business! All of the bags! Now, please, attach yourselves to the cables, join me up here and let us meet in person!", 
["addation_0f7cca6641878f9d"] = "Great it\'s open! Get Taxman outta there.", 
["addation_729197445654a0ef"] = "Put the idiots out of their misery!", 
["addation_3f0149508b0c7106"] = "It looks like someone at Murkywater might be behind our current predicament. They have closed all communication channels with me.  Still got a couple friends there, but it looks like I am officially... ousted. Mr. Lindenhurst was kind enough to decrypt some notes an ancestor had printed on the back of a painting:The View of Mount Vernon. Bain owned the real thing you know; you have to wonder how he pulled that one off, yeah? Watookal, the notes detail that inside the vault of the Brooklyn Bank, there\'s something buried in the foundation; something that Bain needed, put there when the concrete was poured. I\'ve no idea what it is, and how all this fits together, but whoever got to him put in a lot of resources, so it\'s probably not any old dinges. We\'re going in to get it before anyone else finds out, yeah?", 
["addation_8db5dc302d16eec6"] = "OK, take a look around and see if you can find something to get us past that gate.", 
["addation_5372f81bc2b86d45"] = "You guys are great! I\'m your number one fan!", 
["addation_73e4cfaf1465dd4f"] = "That\'s the last one! Perfect!", 
["addation_3137efc2ffc63213"] = "Where is it!?", 
["addation_6522b8275c31f001"] = "Hey, the escape chopper is here. If you feel lucky you can go get the rest of the bags - otherwise get out!", 
["addation_417712112f83cd05"] = "That explosion will have it raining crystals for weeks. ", 
["addation_e62d7b8fac8dbd1a"] = "Remember what I said: don\'t kill the guard. Your nonsense won\'t trick the Control-Guy again and he\'ll sound the alarm.", 
["addation_17bf8649a56000ee"] = "All this waiting is fucking killing me!", 
["addation_b0f084f3628b0a9c"] = "Fucking hell!", 
["addation_3317e01b27b6f7ba"] = "No bullets with Garrett\'s name on them tonight, OK friends?", 
["addation_3649e8832bf2337a"] = "You\'ve got to keep at least 4 bags!", 
["addation_783f37c86c61bfe9"] = "Hilary at Gensec here. Routine check. Can I have the time lock codes?", 
["addation_971a697b6ac90040"] = "I can only take two at a time...", 
["addation_d49dd9077f9a697c"] = "PEOC maintenance, we are currently unable to assist. Please try again later.", 
["addation_5bfe6d35f629720c"] = "You couldn\'t stop yourself, could you? Well, the world\'s a better place without that bastard, but Wick will be disappointed he wasn\'t part of it, so you better leave the other one for him.", 
["addation_cbad89d155f9dfee"] = "Get him in the back!", 
["addation_b9e1a07f126d846c"] = "Right, now you got to get it open. See if you can find a tool around there somewhere to help do the job, yeah?", 
["addation_6d5c122d1847c74a"] = "We\'re stuck without that keycard. Find Ralph garnet!", 
["addation_7d29f14543e272cd"] = "Picked up a tail!", 
["addation_7d68177f82d1c8b9"] = "Only way back is forward, people!", 
["addation_9e2705df23273840"] = "Keep them away from the device if you can.", 
["addation_bee04c4f3413f33e"] = "You just keep it up. This is text book stuff.", 
["addation_3f2696e95538700f"] = "Careful! The roof is about to collapse!", 
["addation_1e5badc7c0817694"] = "... the head honcho loves detail-oriented motherfuckers!", 
["addation_cf0a8e8a40ce932f"] = "Someone heard the drill!", 
["addation_348306864afb71f4"] = "Stay completely still and keep your hands in the air.", 
["addation_96ab207882b87c9a"] = "Run! Run!", 
["addation_4f28b93a5cd6338e"] = "That gear\'s expensive. Like, ten years of your salary expensive. Deal with the fire!", 
["addation_9212263168aa0d96"] = "Please man, I\'m just a rookie.", 
["addation_8d212c5687dd5977"] = "Ah, don\'t wet your knickers, Bain! I have buyer. Very far away. Is all good. ", 
["addation_fb9ea8f9845584de"] = "The place was under surveillance! We are going for the bridge!", 
["addation_9e97869719a87be2"] = "You\'re keeping it quiet. Great. Remember - you need the keycard.", 
["addation_dc70d960453777ef"] = "Another guard up ahead. Stay in the shadows.", 
["addation_cccc3546dd610a03"] = "OK...", 
["addation_d0394997b06abb9d"] = "Alright, fuck it...", 
["addation_c57cd1e8c5b91beb"] = "A police chopper is coming in to drop of sniper on a nearby building.", 
["addation_1bdec82bf9d44256"] = "Keep a low profile though. Never know who is looking.", 
["addation_d59cdc5c8a31a647"] = "OK, forget the window cleaning platform, you\'re going to have to use ziplines to move the bags out!", 
["addation_3f41df91ba42c82a"] = "Still silent. Nice. Find the radio.", 
["addation_114b03efb44e3c76"] = "I believe the Sosa Cartel may now be regretting their decision to try to intimidate me. Their Miami operation now lies in ruins, and I can do business in peace again. Thank you for delivering my message.", 
["addation_a009dc7be549f242"] = "On my way, boss!", 
["addation_6e3113ce5ecc9e07"] = "The process is done! Bag it up, and lets do another round.", 
["addation_ccea0698d3bb13bb"] = "Pick up the pace, head for the library.", 
["addation_b13e2d7744df5623"] = "Let\'s empty this bank out, starting with the safe deposit boxes... Lots of mysteries in there I bet...", 
["addation_49d643e8abf1af99"] = "Ah crap. The plane\'s got to ditch. Alright, we\'re switching plans.", 
["addation_7278d1b4aa61a0f5"] = "Ah, you got it wrong. Maybe bringing hazmat suits would have been a good idea. Wait until it stops reacting, then try again.", 
["addation_cd7187f656a106c4"] = "Alright, we\'re in for deposit boxes.", 
["addation_69fb3f5df62555c4"] = "Well you heard Hector. No time to piss around. We go into the meth lab and secure the goods. ", 
["addation_e637d3a12a7faf14"] = "Damn, BFD is bust. You need tools to fix her up.", 
["addation_88eeda6f1bd6fa9b"] = "All right, entry point. Synchronize on my mark... mark.", 
["addation_8b44fd8a5fd78537"] = "Second keycard can\'t be far. Gotta be nearby. Keep looking.", 
["addation_f336c23299dbb203"] = "That\'s the vault, for sure.", 
["addation_c36bb9d604ccaad2"] = "Incoming call to the PEOC. Put me through and hope we haven\'t been discovered.", 
["addation_d775d7bc52775da6"] = "Time to make a hasty retreat guys.", 
["addation_55121245459e1a5b"] = "The winch is where it needs to be, but I need your help attaching the magnet.", 
["addation_457e76115e3e6196"] = "There\'s the pilot. Christ, that old soak can barely stand, let alone fly a plane. Escort him somewhere safe. I\'ll get the chopper on the way.", 
["addation_1eb3fc9d78171e33"] = "You made us come for nothing?", 
["addation_db4631da79b9aabb"] = "Dammit! SWAT ambush. I didn\'t see it!", 
["addation_96977894b277363f"] = "You\'re all down, yes? No broken ankles? Good. Now find the first money pallet. They\'re there somewhere. Find em, and light a flare. ", 
["addation_63ddc284a4696b3b"] = "Almost there now, just a few more bags and we should have enough.", 
["addation_705a275d7d7c1a7e"] = "Hey, hold your horses. Take this blowtorch. You\'re gonna need it to get inside.", 
["addation_848d4ef7c81ae947"] = "You know, me and the King? We flew around town, picked up chicks left and right, you know. I was paying for most of the stuff obviously.", 
["addation_35ab34fb376d3053"] = "Can I come out yet? Are they gone?", 
["addation_22b47fbf57246371"] = "Blowing the walling will wreck the ballot machines. Accident, right? We\'re just doing an honest bank heist.", 
["addation_2acd01780c7503d3"] = "Up! Up! Up, up, up!", 
["addation_53462bbe9dc4abad"] = "I\'m moving out.", 
["addation_8f11bb97b7305843"] = "OK, solid.", 
["addation_2cecb441fe66a54e"] = "...you will find it in a dumpster out by the construction site, friends.", 
["addation_c9d486484b548470"] = "Thats him! Dont let him escape!", 
["addation_9ed80867f2ed3ad9"] = "Forget what you just saw and concentrate on counting your reward! The Big Eight send their regards.", 
["addation_4aa4ff5760e043d2"] = "I guess they\'re not very picky about quality of life...", 
["addation_2ce6eae5789bd899"] = "Ok gang. My mole in the police will take care of this. He\'ll send his guys to clean up and then report that the area was searched and they found nothing. No one will know you\'re here, you can relax.", 
["addation_5d9fc54e2c5e5ac9"] = "Getting the money is fine, but your priority has to be assembling the skyhook. Look for the pieces of the cage and get it built.", 
["addation_2a90e87626134eaa"] = "Well, looks like we have some crafty litte thieves, trying to steal our money. Put them down.", 
["addation_fa3dc6365e46d9e0"] = "Server room - find it.", 
["addation_1c8f0b3371bd5095"] = "Get ready to drop Floyd. Yeah, I named him Floyd.", 
["addation_f232926b669c305a"] = "Cops sent in a chopper with heavy tactical units. Bite down cuz this is gonna sting.", 
["addation_0336380b73cceebe"] = "Loot for the taking...", 
["addation_ef2d41ce0ade7ec9"] = "Plane\'s nearly there. Pop the flares and mark the strip.", 
["addation_7ba0bacad68a5129"] = "Now let it do it\'s thing, and remember to keep the cops off it.", 
["addation_6be078e5f49323cb"] = "Starting my approach. ETA four minutes. Over.", 
["addation_bfddae6737455641"] = "You made it! It\'s right there! Grab the diamond!", 
["addation_ee195f8c2830707e"] = "You did good. Better than I thought you would, to be honest. We got what we came for, and I bet we can get a good payday from that gold you stole. Should be more than enough to get you started again.", 
["addation_e234d735df5f7466"] = "Heads up, SWATs are moving in to try to finish this.", 
["addation_4fa04be2f3e319a9"] = "The dropzone will be long gone if you don\'t hurry. Jump!", 
["addation_747b4980c9283e15"] = "Another twelve and we\'re done!", 
["addation_b67d6c283c9de9c1"] = "Maybe he put it somewhere really obvious, yeah?", 
["addation_16951ac49589a42a"] = "Okay. The controls. Hack \'em, and keep the cops off.", 
["addation_65d128ef14f4634c"] = "Maybe something historical, yeah?", 
["addation_b5df682304ad6824"] = "You trying to pull a fast one on us, huh?", 
["addation_5a7386a558abd647"] = "I think that is the armor of Oda Nabunaga. This is serious loot, gang. Load up!", 
["addation_35432f7381588b5d"] = "You can\'t get the code without any juice. Get the power turned on again!", 
["addation_2ad79e379fee0d6f"] = "Perhaps... muriatic acid?", 
["addation_0279dd45f556f84a"] = "This area has several vaults, which can be opened from a control room. We want what\'s in the vaults so necessity demands we get to the control room.", 
["addation_1ea92bdbb6b6859e"] = "Great, Set off the flare so the chopper can land!", 
["addation_03a3ce7e4bf27285"] = "This is the boat. I see the lights, I\'m on my way.", 
["addation_39d9ab228c42931b"] = "You\'ll be needing that torch later for sure.", 
["addation_5172f9a5be93af0d"] = "This is a warning. We are authorised to kill and your time is up. Your move, creeps.", 
["addation_3485a8f9ce86990d"] = "The panic is on the third floor. Get over there. ", 
["addation_70b95d767eb656ce"] = "I\'ve left you a keycard, an arc cutter and some breaching charges, my friends. I could press a button and open a door, but we must hide my involvement, yes.", 
["addation_dc5c5b4f4c1bcc1d"] = "Ok now, which transport is he in? Saw them all open and find out!", 
["addation_0685a5910cfb2dd6"] = "We\'re not going in by the main entrance. You see that fence? That\'s our way in.", 
["addation_04d224e0a29cde0a"] = "Was banking on you saying yes. I\'ll try again later.", 
["addation_ffa0878c45e40c1d"] = "Find some way past the gates without raising any suspicions.", 
["addation_09161db340b5edc3"] = "I\'m pleased, but I\'m not surprised.", 
["addation_849871e241424e8c"] = "There\'s a car waiting for you, just across the road.", 
["addation_e1fc9a6f0b86a327"] = "There\'s a conveyor chute over there. It can carry the loot to....let me check.", 
["addation_dd9ee572813f480a"] = "I\'m in. Need some time to open that lock. Instead of sitting there scratching your ass, head out to the van and get some C4. Time to prepare your escape.", 
["addation_b2eb21abf61e7e4a"] = "Time to grab the money guys!", 
["addation_35e2c36edab60dbc"] = "The front door. Easiest way in, hardest way out. ", 
["addation_1de29a99e5f34b9b"] = "The warehouse is where you\'re most likely to find a crowbar.", 
["addation_17eec8431c31beff"] = "Go find Ralph Garnet and take that keycard from his priviledged-ass-self.", 
["addation_534c1eef2a6afb94"] = "OK, let\'s move to the next part of the plan.", 
["addation_1fe1cd7dea018c28"] = "That\'s the head of security. Hmm... he\'s by the driveway I think.", 
["addation_e64104b6bd5619c3"] = "There seems to be some movement in the area. Looks like more bikers. ", 
["addation_fe92b86c1b9b6e3a"] = "That\'s it, gang. That should take care of the gas in the scanning room.", 
["addation_60ad52b3376c3d33"] = "There you go. Now, plug it into a computer.", 
["addation_f65ac12d22f75277"] = "Alright, get to the house and find the address, be careful.", 
["addation_4b67be7613cfcabe"] = "Vlad needs you to secure those bags in the chimney.", 
["addation_0591a2579e961766"] = "The gun needs to charge before you can fire it. Look around for a control panel in there.", 
["addation_d98ddef35875442d"] = "How the fuck did they know we were gonna be here!?", 
["addation_0745a081893aff77"] = "C\'mon, you need to disable the firewall at the other computer.", 
["addation_3fe61009bc0e2113"] = "Move that server! Move it! Come on! ", 
["addation_34f922be0f6f64a6"] = "Ralph just showed himself. Keep you eyes open!", 
["addation_8c81a7737e81781d"] = "Ach, I\'ve got some bad news. They\'re shutting down the air space! You gotta get out of there ASAP!", 
["addation_ce6c784d7ba9100a"] = "Nah, we\'ll keep everything!", 
["addation_52a5e95f620caf93"] = "Thought you guys were stable? What the fuck happened back there?", 
["addation_30e83f579381dbd5"] = "Commissar is throwing everything he has left! Even his damned gunship! Keep your distance!", 
["addation_0336a0e4fdbbb39e"] = "Get the mechanic to start working on Rust\'s bike. Just do as he says and get him what he needs.", 
["addation_49315b9393500b17"] = "Cameras will set of the mines, guys! Stay away!", 
["addation_4c75cecdbba7f69b"] = "SWATS are going for the ground floor, left staircase.", 
["addation_6721d727c7a14dd9"] = "Okay guys, at the right moment, disrupt the deal. Then Alex lifts the limo outta there. Ready now!", 
["addation_a830766d1eb41655"] = "That\'ll do for Gage, but you can stay for more.", 
