["addation_8f285f22e118bf98"] = "There\'s a traitor, close to the group. Or in it. I know there is.", 
["addation_22fed5e5fb4eec63"] = "Hop on the chopper friends! Bile wants to make like a tree and get out of there!", 
["addation_ed5016934031ff65"] = "Your next target is the voting machines. I\'ll bet they\'re stored in sealed crates. You clowns will need to improvise to open them.", 
["addation_83e3c05617215c2f"] = "...muriatic acid?", 
["addation_33dde7a224b0916e"] = "So guys, where\'s that laptop?", 
["addation_05a18bfcd689fee2"] = "Make sure you find the right wine!", 
["addation_2a44d7641a8bc88b"] = "Head up to the apartment, my associate has the info and the cash for the extra meth.", 
["addation_367264160d865fde"] = "Search those crates. Should be some C4 in one of them.", 
["addation_d887d8146dfa8af3"] = "Happy birthday. Vault full of freshly loaded safe deposit boxes. Who\'s in?", 
["addation_be647a188391caa7"] = "Alright, we got the address for where the Commissar\'s at. It\'s an old apartment complex. Place is a run-down dump. Hard to say what security you can expect. Suit up, and let\'s finish this.", 
["addation_571d54f0d48797ec"] = "...and cross your fingers.", 
["addation_64de006d524a6dda"] = "The game is on, motherfuckers!", 
["addation_5d0227b15e2f1216"] = "Freaking Ralph. Spoiled prick. Too good for his own party.", 
["addation_173e504168ea657b"] = "SWAT\'s have deployed to the adjacent roofs, so watch the crossfire.", 
["addation_ee93a0d227e0af13"] = "Violence is always an option. Prosecute it longer with this.", 
["addation_d9c4457f53c94b71"] = "There you go, now find that laptop and hack it.", 
["addation_ccb7b4926fd4646f"] = "I see one!", 
["addation_7185a15c8b6d236d"] = "Alright, we don\'t know which prison transport our man is in, so you\'d better place a saw on each one of the four trucks!", 
["addation_81f32d170d2ab42c"] = "Put the stuff in the car...", 
["addation_bf171df863cb6571"] = "Look for the standard reinforced door. That should access the security room.", 
["addation_4fd25ce4c5a4c28d"] = "First thing, get inside.", 
["addation_e465c8a25cb5f8b8"] = "Patching in Vlad...", 
["addation_0f4c26c4af12fffc"] = "Vault keycard. It gets half the job done. Swipe it in the reader, and then track down the second card.", 
["addation_93fbbd040b464eae"] = "Great, lets take a peek under the hood. Hmmm, nice. Good security, but nothing I can\'t handle.", 
["addation_494eb3297e6300f3"] = "The surveillance operator is down. Those cameras shouldn\'t bother you anymore!", 
