["addation_662ea9bec54e0939"] = "Coming in at the back, my masked friends. I\'ll only stay a short while so bring me anything you want to secure, and do it fast.", 
["addation_c83f1fbb3ac4ea55"] = "I guess that\'s the server room. Make note of it - you should find the cash first.", 
