["addation_35481b620c912557"] = "They\'re going to keep sending harder kerels, friends.", 
["addation_d00a16f42568cfb5"] = "Oh, shit, shit, I forgot something. Listen, If you find any tapes, take them too please... I don\'t know maybe burn them somewhere later, OK?", 
["addation_fed45c757f5d8bcd"] = "We got wind of a mountain of coke on the top floor. They\'ll do everything to keep you off that stash. Get to it before the Commissar destroys it. You know what they say: "The early bird catches the grade-a product".", 
