["addation_892464914dab93b9"] = "Then we just need to go in to get the gold.", 
["addation_19d0c46921328115"] = "There\'s an access hatch to the sewers over by the gas station. Go there, and get down.", 
["addation_372992cf09a6c60d"] = "Woah, we lost some loot in that explosion! Well, no time to waste! Look trough the rest of the deposit boxes.", 
["addation_7cdb5bbe91dc26b4"] = "Does everyone understand the plan?", 
