["addation_d633bbcab486b7f8"] = "Excellent. They are blind! Blind as a bat. Though bats are supposed to be blind, and locate prey by echolocation, so that is...", 
["addation_779fae849dad150e"] = "What\'re you waiting for?", 
["addation_a385ab165ec17ed5"] = "My old protection business must start up. It is taken, and customers need change of mind.", 
["addation_22237312f19fd64f"] = "Now check the screen for the code, then go and open the vault.", 
["addation_2e9eec4f593b636e"] = "Hahaha that was kiff! Now get going, friends!", 
["addation_243e60d674d1e206"] = "Alright. Finally, we\'re going after the rat - the fink who screwed Hox, wants to screw us all. Time to put him down. We know he\'s currently bunkering down in an FBI safe house outside the city. These safe houses are usually built along the same lines. Nice big houses, grounds, 24 hour security, and most likely a panic room somewhere inside. See where your tax dollars go? The plan is simple - get in there, find our informer and finish him. Now, I\'m betting there\'ll be evidence against us in there too, so be good to clean that up too.", 
["addation_be28038528de000d"] = "SWATS are driving in from the west, on Pacific Drive.", 
["addation_b768522be37718d9"] = "These fuckers went to driving school - I\'ll tell you that much!", 
["addation_8d76f0dfe45a2563"] = "These idiots must have had it here somewhere.", 
["addation_b0c49cd28b319e48"] = "You guys OK in there?", 
["addation_f8a8b260974195a0"] = "OK, the special ingredient for the vault we\'re going to use is liquid nitrogen, courtesy of Mr Blonde.", 
["addation_c91453abc9ffe43e"] = "Of course. Thanks for being understanding. Take care. In the clear, gang.", 
["addation_a7abbd39748cdde2"] = "Another successful acquisition! Well done, my friends!", 
["addation_515e27a20c76efb6"] = "The Mendozas are down there. Cut that fence and get those guns.", 
["addation_61fbcfa447c421ff"] = "Two-Five-Zero-Zero-Zero, half way! Keep going!", 
["addation_81aa1e41f7144145"] = "Nice. Now get that evidence to the lab. Any DNA might help us finger this rat.", 
["addation_7aa6eaae8a9a86d8"] = "They had no chance at all. I don\'t think the National Guard could have stopped you.", 
["addation_6144d5863fe00d77"] = "Now load up on C4. You\'ll need it.", 
["addation_76e8b3c77b3353cf"] = "Just food for the rats now.", 
["addation_59b300331669036b"] = "We had agreed on more than this.", 
["addation_2b4b570e40de642d"] = "I see one!", 
["addation_21eaa19a7afc5d47"] = "Dammit, the cops disabled the hacking device! You need to reboot it!", 
["addation_221495efcbfa8f90"] = "This place is running low on supplies. If you wanna go for more ingredients, signal the chopper with a flare. This pilot\'s on the clock, so make it worth while. Or you can bounce. Your call.", 
["addation_67737ee931913389"] = "YES FRIENDS! Oh, sorry... I\'m not used to this sneaking about, yeah?", 
["addation_a794ee0527b4d6c2"] = "I will arrange for my associate to be there.", 
["addation_677a3791e4fb229a"] = "There\'s millions of files here and they\'re all encrypted. Get him talking again!", 
["addation_777ca70b4abe5a56"] = "Gonna punch your ticket for ya!", 
["addation_454f71ef90405ae1"] = "We\'ve got your money right here. The info is in the safe. I\'ll open it. No funny shit or you die.", 
["addation_b115c22bbfc2ada2"] = "Everything\'s locked down - if you want me to fix it then I need to get into the surveillance room.", 
["addation_599c51e8862d401d"] = "Got this bucket of bolts pinned!", 
["addation_ad4d496a02085d04"] = "Mitchell\'s over by the pool.", 
["addation_086c04dd93875fd3"] = "Get at the vault, you\'ll need to get past security.", 
["addation_df12148dc73e2439"] = "Die you bastards!", 
