["addation_b6d3afad7c299789"] = "Good move.. that\'s bound to lead to the warehouse.", 
["addation_95854d61b392c8f5"] = "...Kerels right around the corner, friends.", 
["addation_3f0b41154333a862"] = "Guys, we need to talk about what happened up in Alaska, but I\'ve got another job first, while you\'re still out west. So, the son of an old friend of mine in L.A., member of the Cabot crime family needs help hitting a jewelry store for a haul of diamonds. I owe him big from years ago, when his dad got me out of a jam, so I promised him a little extra muscle as payback. These guys are pro\'s, real characters. They even use code names! You guys up for it?", 
["addation_4cac7b5329a0f5b3"] = "Keep it together, keep it up.", 
["addation_5d86cd77595ff567"] = "Now pop the manhole! We\'re getting out through the sewers!", 
["addation_3e02f47b72d5d1cc"] = "Yeah. He was the King, but I was the fucking Ceasar, you know.", 
["addation_b8cbe9aa3d2a4007"] = "Smile for the camera, assholes. I see you. Yes.", 
