["addation_c29993c54cfb811f"] = "One of the items we are here for is being kept in the warehouse archive. You can use the crane in the central hub to get it, once you find the right shelf.", 
["addation_55e8012167e680ef"] = "Ah, my friends. So, the "mules", you see...well, they\'re actually goats. And they\'ve..errr, escaped. Find them for me.", 
