["addation_22241ebcfd33229c"] = "We\'re using crates to get you into the Commissar\'s place. Trojan horse style. His apartment is a cruddy dump in a crappy part of town. Security ain\'t great, but I\'m sure he and his muscle have something in their back pocket. Objective is simple: find the Commissar and kill him. This is going to get loud, so dress to impress.", 
["addation_7bdae2ee157ee238"] = "We\'re watchdogs on this job. Wear a heavy jacket and carry heavier weapons. We know Hector\'s transports are getting hit. You\'ll ride in the back of the truck. Don\'t let the coke go anywhere.", 
["addation_80f501324f06c3ef"] = "My money would be on the buildings having the keycards. Search \'em.", 
["addation_6f3fdc731f6a7538"] = "Please, head to the Black Ridge facility in Nevada. It has Murkywater loot for you to steal.", 
["addation_977384440139a2db"] = "Hurry now, secure the artifact on the chopper!", 
["addation_3423dbbe325f71f0"] = "Let me remind you - you need to be wiping out the mobsters. Search the motel.", 
["addation_6ef138da13cc074e"] = "They\'re on the roof!", 
["addation_56d361bc33070c8e"] = "There you go. That\'s our target. Keep it safe and out of trouble.", 
["addation_37c0d1d7c4c3594f"] = "Good work, now watch \'em overheat. You\'ll get that system reboot.", 
["addation_4fa621a0a5601e79"] = "No! Dammit, gang... Wick wanted to take care of them himself. He really had it in for these bastards. I guess he will have to be content with the idea of them dead.", 
["addation_027636c72fbf5348"] = "Let\'s find a way into the prison.", 
["addation_f589027b6305b5c4"] = "Outside!", 
["addation_7a3938a6a5ba6741"] = "Here she comes. "BFD". Stands for "Big Goddamn Drill". Almost.", 
["addation_2ab184897e82f8d7"] = "Boom! Good! Now, inside. Skop, skiet en boomklim!", 
["addation_3e9f7b7d55079ed0"] = "Oh, shiny! Whoever looted this liked the finer stuff.", 
["addation_6a3ffb385f263135"] = "Come on, let\'s get going. Get in.", 
["addation_c7c0f8370b81e5f6"] = "An Armory! It\'s locked down, but a keycard should get you inside. Should be plenty of ammo in there.", 
["addation_2e3ff35ac461f399"] = "I\'ve had it with these guys!", 
["addation_4fb69321ddd0fd41"] = "Should I send a team over to help you look?", 
