["addation_739d0f609505fac2"] = "There\'s no turning back - get out of this goddamn place!", 
["addation_daf5819b65941490"] = "Time to start looking for that stash of Murky loot. We\'re looking for cash, and lots of it. ", 
["addation_2a5241649c66f793"] = "C\'mon friends, no standing around.", 
["addation_8512286f56c5c18a"] = "We\'re done, let\'s move and get out!", 
["addation_860854ed66917e32"] = "Thermite\'s done its job. Now hook that water pump up to the vault.", 
["addation_52199dd2a432aadf"] = "Check the backrooms.", 
["addation_3a4c822c71dcb1f6"] = "You got to take \'em out! They\'re fucking killing me!", 
["addation_715a5e2c987ae2c0"] = "What the fuck is this!?", 
["addation_d0e6b004e5a32899"] = "Got your box. Get over here! Get that crap stowed.", 
["addation_0c1f397fa51ac9d4"] = "Two minutes.", 
["addation_b43e0f1386d216b9"] = "Crap. You guys seeing this? Something went up there. Pyro team - fix it!", 
["addation_7f322be91d1b7bc4"] = "Set the zip-line up on the roof, then haul ass to the crane.", 
["addation_a99916bfbb3a68a0"] = "Go inside and see if there\'s a clue to the code anywhere.", 
["addation_63653b6b23fa90fc"] = "I can\'t get the door open if you don\'t cover me!", 
["addation_fcd2739f9d805fae"] = "Hell yeah. Those missiles are perfect. Take them to the radar. ", 
["addation_fd5f38aa34654a0f"] = "Surrender your arms. Sniper have your every move. Do not force us to use deadly force again.", 
["addation_b0c394f920c23e5b"] = "I don\'t know, something\'s not right here... Next time I\'ll sound the alarm.", 
["addation_a2ce53867c2ca40f"] = "Ok, that takes care of the cameras.", 
["addation_209a5f8e0c80b2c6"] = "SWATs incoming from the lumber mill, keep them away!", 
["addation_38c840d909e7e441"] = "Thanks, I\'ll have my man here inspect it and if it\'s the right one we\'re good to go. So hang tight for a second.", 
["addation_947b917599c76fa2"] = "Everyone, you know how it\'s done. Some surveillance would be smart. Drill the vault when you\'re ready. I don\'t know what\'s here but I like our chances.", 
["addation_70c5c15b7f4ee234"] = "Ach, you gotta get into that thing somehow. Wasn\'t really prepared for that.", 
["addation_94c352ecea329347"] = "Right, this is the place. Get to the traincar and look for your contact. They said they\'d meet you there. So far it all looks good. Just trade the paintings and get out fast. Keep it rolling.", 
["addation_47dc23f56503ddd8"] = "Guys, don\'t let the cops take the coke!", 
["addation_5cb59501ee5e49ad"] = "Okay, now wait for the pilot.", 
["addation_e215e8cafe9f40b1"] = "There he is!", 
["addation_daba922d568cfc3f"] = "Don\'t just stand around, get in there. ", 
["addation_3cc621c842ae0e49"] = "Check between the trains too, guys. Don\'t get sloppy.", 
["addation_8c9949133b61be38"] = "OK! Chopper\'s here! Go!", 
["addation_4cdf1e1415a866ea"] = "Don\'t be overeager gang, store\'s not going anywhere.", 
["addation_4fe1b6488c567e1b"] = "That\'s the depot where the machines are kept. Move out, you clowns.", 
["addation_2c5fc9e839c4cc3d"] = "Hurry, they might destroy the intelligence before you have time to reach it!", 
["addation_4ed9526eba0a9cd9"] = "Great. Now, ready to bail? Just meet our Insider man. She\'ll show you the way out.", 
["addation_6e225c83c7abbd61"] = "You need to guard the cannon.", 
["addation_399cc25570878260"] = "Murkywater\'s been moving stuff through DC by convoy for months. I\'ve resisted hitting these til we got a shot at a big prize. Here it is. Gold bullion. Got a "diversion" on the Woodrow set up to get it where we want it, then we\'re gonna seperate an armored truck from an armed convoy. Once it\'s isolated, hit it and boost that sweet bling. Au yeah.", 
["addation_1e378bd87764aff7"] = "You\'ve been good little heisters. Here, have a gift.", 
["addation_460ffeab0cca5c18"] = "Ag man, that wasn\'t very nice!", 
["addation_7300eb6b55993ca2"] = "You gotta get into that tunnel, friends. ", 
["addation_84a409be2aa4c25a"] = "Public office. Wow, we are in the wrong line of work gentlemen.", 
["addation_e1e2ef92abc74200"] = "All right, that should do it! Coming in.", 
["addation_64563e1edfd03490"] = "The deal went through. You can make the trade now.", 
["addation_1e010842021bb6ed"] = "Sorry, friends. Looks like we didn\'t get you in clean. The place is on alert and locked down.", 
["addation_c76b49f44d0168a1"] = "The drill is almost done. Stand by, gang.", 
["addation_8cf1cbee5a287c40"] = "Do what you need to do to hold back the tide!", 
["addation_d9d692854b64179c"] = "This algorithm will wreak havoc on their servers.", 
["addation_f323591ced985433"] = "Damn, they\'ve upgraded to the Mark 7 detectors. Going to be a bit more difficult.", 
["addation_8622e43e53b269e2"] = "I think we can make more cuts, yeah. We don\'t need all these tellers.  Who gives a rats ass if people queue for an hour!", 
["addation_e9e8ec259adfc7f7"] = "Portable computers. Times three.", 
["addation_22b6efcfb17b1b52"] = "We have information about the Mendoza cashflow. Over $100 million from their American operations. We want to send a message - their money and their weapons are null and void.", 
["addation_549c161d0c2bb209"] = "Well, look... I\'m going to send some guys over there to check on things.", 
["addation_79068d073c3cbecd"] = "Okay, gang. Elephant gave you the briefing, so you know what we\'re after. We need to find the BCI headset and the computer software. You manage this, we\'ll make a lot of money.", 
["addation_710b7016647f19f3"] = "Great. Now, blow the doors!", 
["addation_1fef6960d46185b5"] = "Put the idiots out of their misery!", 
["addation_c8586aebdc6dc2b4"] = "You need to shoot the gas can to set it on fire!", 
["addation_2ea73783f9aa80ea"] = "I\'m sure they\'re going to be well-guarded.", 
["addation_7235f789055948d0"] = "Gate won\'t open with you standing on it, genius. Clear the area!", 
["addation_cf9af027ca5631ff"] = "Not much further now. Get him up the tower on the right!", 
["addation_de3f3aa926306906"] = "No good dropping vials, guys.", 
["addation_267d767edcd59ae7"] = "I got real bad news!", 
["addation_2aca63a6ceab3810"] = "Up top!", 
["addation_c13b584feba1ec08"] = "Alright. The cage is put together. But it\'s empty. Get it filled!", 
["addation_cdf5fe2dbb2fb1ec"] = "Hey, hurry up will you!", 
["addation_8be5dbea69f50e03"] = "Damn! Someone must have found the body! Take him out before he sounds the alarm!", 
["addation_d9512fdfd3a40211"] = "Careful with the head!", 
["addation_d7cfd8b8386af25d"] = "Is there a problem over there?", 
["addation_7c410108b30ff51c"] = "Alesso is playing at the Gensec arena. We\'re going to teach them that nothing can stop the Payday Gang.", 
["addation_c6770ba141ad8695"] = "Did me first stint at Strangeways. Just did me last. I\'m not going back, lads.", 
["addation_f82a798003dc8608"] = "That\'s a lot of shiny. Worth a fortune, but we just have to get it open. See if you can find any clues to those symbols around there.", 
["addation_452ec3eb31fae79f"] = "Get those screws off that thing.", 
["addation_04c680ffa05503a3"] = "Something wrong with pump.", 
["addation_1d07f7583cd91264"] = "Better get moving boys, the longer it takes the more cops are going to show up!", 
["addation_f41b31a80a252484"] = "I\'ve arranged a false pager for a first-year resident, but first you need to get hold of a patient file.", 
["addation_a1f4c72e4dc37f90"] = "Now let\'s finish this. Into the manhole, guys! Time for a sewer escape.", 
["addation_c83f5df532c99d2e"] = "In the building!", 
["addation_f6462e32fde558d9"] = "Great, moneys coming down.", 
["addation_927adb265b2566f2"] = "OK, good. Now take care of the other router.", 
["addation_5fc99e35014e950e"] = "Better you guys than me, yeah?", 
["addation_25473a515c77ddde"] = "*Cries*", 
["addation_7c94137dd67d2235"] = "That is the first of some fucking sweet loot! Excellent! Now, you will find a large vertical shaft nearby. Send loot up it by cable. I will look after it.", 
["addation_a508fe4bac8e14c9"] = "Mr Sturr, comply or we will be forced to take you down.", 
["addation_edc24edec22fa039"] = "Hey, thanks for the rescue guys. Best of luck to ya.", 
["addation_23e3f9436427414e"] = "Good job! Carry on.", 
["addation_1b2d89d1ba3e373c"] = "Quickly now, to the weapons lab!", 
["addation_dd0658a6cb83c508"] = "Your job is to make them go down without a goddam fight!", 
["addation_e6e7791644ce47cd"] = "Yes! Yes! Now it\'s time to see helmets flying!", 
["addation_1d64f793330543f6"] = "Guys, please. A professional man needs his snack when working. Get me that coke and make the mechanic a happy man.", 
["addation_8f3cd103ec0aba9b"] = "I\'ll tell you what. We were never gonna deal with you guys! We\'ll take it all!", 
["addation_6eb5b8f406d38b40"] = "Get the hell out!", 
["addation_6a8f55df33f4efd9"] = "Bam! That\'s one less flank to worry about.", 
["addation_77f846e5575f6c88"] = "What the hell! Cops just breached another way in.", 
["addation_283cdc458720a41c"] = "There\'s one of the closets. Get picking that lock.", 
["addation_a5a82ea2af75faac"] = "Blerrie! It... worked? Ha! Ok, now use it to get past the gates.", 
["addation_16ca1cb74848d9b0"] = "No way out the front. Quick! Get into the container. You\'re leaving with the loot. Don\'t think about the drop, okay?", 
["addation_34ab40f905b55b7e"] = "Alright, bring it to the van, it\'s right around the corner.", 
["addation_a72be4f482315e87"] = "What the hell, I\'ll do you guys a favor.", 
["addation_f45aba38884be950"] = "Bring more, this is not all of it.", 
["addation_02216f2183372c89"] = "There he is!", 
["addation_b735d68645939ff4"] = "Make sure you don\'t leave Charon behind!", 
["addation_72c61d3a43b3a08a"] = "...for sure. Or, most likely.", 
["addation_8c9dff38b506890a"] = "... I\'m back in a little while!", 
["addation_007786808fcebb4b"] = "OK, good. Now... wait a sec... guys... they\'re talking about sending in air support! You gotta hurry...!", 
["addation_cca8fd926a31866c"] = "Cos it was like that, from the moment we woke. All day, every day - hookers and blow.", 
["addation_ba6fe0efe57072ba"] = "Might want to look in the fitness center. I saw something glowing there.", 
["addation_74df091ee806910e"] = "It\'s open! Get the stuff out of the deposit boxes!", 
["addation_48d5acd73dbfbf5a"] = "Is it all there? Nice - get what\'s yours.", 
["addation_df7fab9429c2fb95"] = "There\'s the house. And, somewhere in there, the rat.", 
["addation_c6cfbf1d5ca85e95"] = "Alright! Let\'s get this over with. Put the stuff in the pick-up and you\'ll get what you want.", 
["addation_886271b7b7fd1b8a"] = "Look for something connected to that place.", 
["addation_ee69923141dfe4d3"] = "OK, Bile is racing your way now! ", 
["addation_550e2ce5ace1a208"] = "...If you find a keycard, opening one up would be pretty easy", 
["addation_5513643a82d46937"] = "Here they come, get ready.", 
["addation_b85d2703a9465731"] = "You see that marked door? That\'s one of our closets.", 
["addation_7d0e38f6d3358b0a"] = "OK, friends. Get to the choppa!", 
["addation_e5dae55ef9157d00"] = "Where. Are. The. Shoes? Where?!", 
["addation_c3af73f22aff142c"] = "The guards inside will probably have pagers. You should be careful.", 
["addation_87da7f25f089c167"] = "Great, we got it!", 
["addation_6b4dcbfb96a13ed6"] = "There are so many stupid criminals in the world that to be smart is a relatively easy thing. It only takes deliberation where most would choose action.", 
["addation_9bfef8bca78f8213"] = "Who shuts down a party this early?!", 
["addation_d6f362df764c1f2a"] = "Get on those terminals, gang. We need the comm frequency.", 
["addation_8361c7b80f7503f1"] = "Mr. Sturr if you hear me, don\'t toss them. You are only hurting your chances.", 
["addation_061d618bc2cf4c19"] = "Some C4 on that gas station should send a message. Get to it.", 
["addation_517860e97322751b"] = "Bile\'s chopper should be here soon.", 
["addation_2a5817c63e017400"] = "Hey, that\'s awesome! I\'m investing in Indian steel.", 
["addation_f4f6cd8a58decbd1"] = "Cops coming up on your west side. Construction site.", 
["addation_1ab482fd82b2c695"] = "Big ones and Benjamins. Beautiful!", 
["addation_d5d2f3785a1f0346"] = "That\'s the head of security. He seems to be at the stairs.", 
["addation_07487119abb13624"] = "Lets make sure we get our gold - it\'s our payday too.", 
["addation_e49c7b36a255fbb7"] = "We got enough now...", 
["addation_a404ea6c04865534"] = "He\'s going for the laundry room. Follow him!", 
["addation_195b98d96ba9c16b"] = "30 more seconds, then I\'m out!", 
["addation_7551226eb041a476"] = "Sorry...slight miscalculation. I\'m going to come around and try again.", 
["addation_c6075ae70f24b20c"] = "We\'re gonna make the rest of your life real fucking short!", 
["addation_27cc4827a6f60526"] = "Time to start looking for that stash of Murky loot. We\'re looking for cash, and lots of it. ", 
["addation_ad08bfaff2ab54b8"] = "What\'s that, extra loot? You sure you wanna do that?", 
["addation_dcaac8194fc29079"] = "Get the USB stick from the head of security.", 
["addation_8346996807eead1d"] = "He\'s headed up. Look for the stairways up.", 
["addation_07ba5a144e25d2c5"] = "You know your way around this prison, you know what to do.", 
["addation_9d5465b25eff373e"] = "You saved the mechanic just in time. Now help him off the chair and make him assemble the bike.", 
["addation_9512730596da407b"] = "Guys, listen! When the EMP goes off I most likely won\'t be able to communicate with you for a while. You need to get down to the hidden laboratory via the hatch.", 
["addation_fb6fd1d94f618451"] = "It might\'ve been misplaced- check everywhere!", 
["addation_5ccae0ffc820a911"] = "I can\'t take the snipers out! Help me, yes?", 
["addation_ae5f19a9c3f4998b"] = "That\'s 13 bags!", 
["addation_d29d99a9e29cdc5d"] = "Didn\'t you hear the man, gang? He needs a gas tank and exhaust pipes from the workshop. Get over there and deliver.", 
["addation_d4c11f2c51b45d95"] = "Keep going guys!", 
["addation_7d3dcf2ff553503c"] = "These are some determined fucking law enforcers!", 
["addation_422869ff781c03f5"] = "Hurry back to the warehouse with those diamonds, friends.", 
["addation_87250506bed5ce3f"] = "Heads up, they\'re deploying tactical squads on a nearby roof top.", 
["addation_cda47dfc0b07be8b"] = "Let\'s start moving those money bags to the cage, gang. ", 
["addation_b5096a60a9cbf6ba"] = "Vlad wants a word...", 
["addation_aa02072bb6e31634"] = "The code begins with a nine, according to my source.", 
["addation_b47218d2f3b97954"] = "That was, you know, kind of a big explosion.", 
["addation_ab2323e029641cc7"] = "It\'s muriatic acid.", 
["addation_20a02f704e4d34bc"] = "They\'re in the dark.", 
["addation_fa94cab3340a4887"] = "Good luck on your treasure hunt, guys. And remember, keep it quiet.", 
["addation_259cc82b09ceff5a"] = "OK, looks like they\'ve upgraded not too long ago. Makes this a little bit harder.", 
["addation_5f44a47e40ce9e56"] = "Well, fuck and shit. Cops shut down the vault\'s opening. Get it going again, and kill any fucking kerel that goes near it.", 
["addation_791bd1d6b01ef157"] = "Get that open, and get whatever is in there!", 
["addation_4fb19ffb933cf3e3"] = "I\'ve always wondered why I seem to have such bad luck near wildlife. There\'s always something trying to bite old Locke... And I do nothing but nice things for the little bastards.", 
["addation_f5792bd5dfd40957"] = "There, good. It\'s back up.", 
["addation_5cdd2f8a4d501177"] = ""Ze plane, friends, ze plane!"", 
["addation_fbd6ca47a1c0c019"] = "Get the cocaine from the van!", 
["addation_a9fcd598c42c2017"] = "Okay. Mask up when you\'re ready.", 
["addation_45b80c484e0e0050"] = "You have approximately two minutes before the train reaches the barricade. You hear me? Two minutes.", 
["addation_d1a61107df2a6cd9"] = "Go find the PC in the Glitter Room, but don\'t stop to dance.", 
["addation_5e1a902f6e501347"] = "OK! you\'ve got enough... Or you can stay for more.", 
["addation_0a0a0043c74ba19e"] = "Take that bastard out!", 
["addation_f2ae409c172c4ae7"] = "Bag those gems.", 
["addation_6cf0ea89f84b2e31"] = "There\'s probably a crowbar around here somewhere.", 
["addation_8fe384044cfd16a6"] = "I left a case of thermal paste for you down there. Make sure you grab it. ", 
["addation_a96df5b26aac472d"] = "These frequencies will be useful later on. For now, though, stay focused on the job.", 
["addation_3412cb3944dc7166"] = "I got the manager\'s file here. Looks like the guy was born to wear this black suit.", 
["addation_1eb64f2f824e22c5"] = "Get back to the mainframe.", 
["addation_4ece7bc392d169f4"] = "There in 30 seconds!", 
["addation_b61fc96102c223ee"] = "Might be good to see things from the roofs, huh? For sure. Look for a ladder to get up.", 
["addation_c828d4c23c7c80d0"] = "Ok, the computer is working nice and steady again, hacking the system.", 
["addation_ca8f4d6586fb7187"] = "Safe house vault is going to be a little crowded tonight. Nicely done, folks.", 
["addation_ae4acf363f38013e"] = "Before we do anything else, we gotta get you past the security gate, so go have a look at what we\'re dealing with, yeah?", 
["addation_61c3a0c1c1b219fa"] = "A bit off my game today friends. Missed the software firewall backup. Can you find the correct computer and turn it off? ", 
["addation_fd18538ac28e178f"] = "Listen to me, I have information critical to your survival.", 
["addation_2449044095e3bbae"] = "He\'s heavier than I thought! Now, let\'s go!", 
["addation_5592b9313dba0f3d"] = "Ach! If the kerels are here too, Garrett must be stepping up his game in helping Murky, to go all the way out here. Or he\'s just very pissed with us.", 
["addation_744d2efc036292c0"] = "Bad news, friends. I can\'t come and get you while they have active air defences online. You gotta go and deactivate them!", 
["addation_637f2c52e492a68e"] = "Murkywater are moving some huge currency reserves by cargo plane. I\'ve got an idea to get it.", 
["addation_c9e07104af033660"] = "Fancy place like this will keep the keys secure. Look for a storage room.", 
["addation_0b6a4988d482ec09"] = "Listen here:", 
["addation_2aaa853b724ced94"] = "Good! Next part of the plan now.", 
["addation_5aaf9af369dc535b"] = "Those motel rooms look like good candidates for a little wrecking. Get in there and get your rockstar on. Smash the TV\'s, lamps - anything you can find.", 
["addation_c624c0642aa34412"] = "That was the wrong code, friends! You need to wait for the system to clear.", 
["addation_d51f791ba1282edf"] = "There\'s the alarm. No problem. Plan B. Put on a show, gang.", 
["addation_6bc4eb4dbfc44a4c"] = "You see all those crates? They\'re about to get shipped out directly to the Commissar\'s location. Grab the labels and check them at the reader over there. That should give us Commissar\'s precise location.", 
["addation_7c80bede3f1495a2"] = "I fuckin\' hate hospitals, man. I ever turn into a vegetable, you guys end my ass. ", 
["addation_909fbaea6b7a0e30"] = "You motherfuckin\' shitbirds. Secure your shit up there.", 
["addation_89e486dbd0166634"] = "His blood must be 80% proof. Stay with him, help him.", 
["addation_fe3cebfd522e79db"] = "I\'ll be there in two!", 
["addation_f3e6aab5f9bd3eac"] = "You know what to do!", 
["addation_74fe41bc2d7d8152"] = "Another four and we\'re done.", 
["addation_f1ed18841ae0407c"] = "You got enough. I\'ll get our man on the way.", 
["addation_98731d8111f39050"] = "C\'mon friends. It\'ll be fun. Blast that door.", 
["addation_76800876671de916"] = "Move, move, move!", 
["addation_65b738c4ff23bbe7"] = "Now Hector tells me we need to hit the Mendozas themselves for information. Where they keep their money, in fact.", 
["addation_1756759a9609782d"] = "They have no clue you are there. Now get out of there.", 
["addation_cb5100b155a2afc6"] = "I\'m coming, in two minutes!", 
["addation_827c1b92d9fcd9bc"] = "Got a footman checking out the bank. Make sure he\'s... Welcomed.", 
["addation_d7e41fda8c3ecd1d"] = "Hmm... I don\'t know if that really was the server... ", 
["addation_331337609ecf757b"] = "Kiff! Now go and have a look inside, yeah?", 
["addation_c1d52f2c119b6520"] = "Uh, it was number...", 
["addation_093b9e05dec67f76"] = "Alright, finally!", 
["addation_91f3843c49d791ea"] = "I\'ll be there in 3 minutes.", 
["addation_b3f53d9490be6358"] = "By the time they get new ones out there it\'ll be too late - and there will be no voting in this district. ", 
["addation_de2211e4e5d42fce"] = "Just grab that loot and let\'s get it out of here.", 
["addation_0e8756250cf7a95d"] = "What the fuck\'s happening!?", 
["addation_79560f242c33efd0"] = "You need to find Garrett\'s office.", 
["addation_3b88ef65eac95fca"] = "Just a little longer.", 
["addation_7588e6110d3c076c"] = "No you won\'t, I say nada!", 
