["addation_c990c818902a907b"] = "One time, I was in the jungle with a kak piece of laptop, trying to hack into this ancient security system being run by a bunch of dwankie terrorists. In a very unfortunate event, a snake bites my leg, and I mistakenly activate the alarm, alerting everyone, and making them blow up the entire place. Lots of terrorists died, and no one got paid that day. Blerrie snake...", 
