["addation_d248125bc63c8d6a"] = "Shiiit!", 
["addation_4be6a42ad858dc6e"] = "Fire in the hole!", 
["addation_50d12e8abd32336b"] = "Bravo! Now, second step - find the local security station, cut through and approve the opening sequence.", 
["addation_a74812b2a219ce76"] = "I recognize the two of you, but where is my old fucking mask!?", 
["addation_d5d4cacbbd9cba52"] = "The escape will be there in nine minutes.", 
["addation_a80bfe1a31bc17d5"] = "Since you took care of the outer panic room door, the lance won\'t need as long. At least there\'s that!", 
["addation_1ddc4bad92610afb"] = "Check the back!", 
["addation_b8bade1f99135ef9"] = "Sounds a little unhinged. Best do it.", 
["addation_c2b43cd87a9796f1"] = "Now hook up the detonator, friends.", 
["addation_cc7ad454eeaec5b4"] = "You made a mighty big mistake coming here!", 
["addation_86fa9a96c1a1ed71"] = "The voting results are stored on a nearby server. Find it and scramble that data.", 
["addation_39c469d3ab429ce0"] = "...And take the boxes from the conveyor end, at the entrance. They should be waiting for you, yeah?", 
["addation_f59952c5528536ea"] = "Great!", 
["addation_3fb5c76b90c1e6f9"] = "The Elephant briefed you about the Brain-Computer Interface, right? We\'re after a high-tech headset and a software that allows you to control a drone using your brain. Trust me, I can barely believe it myself. Anyhow, according to Rust, both things are currently being transported on this train.", 
["addation_87a8e1bcc14d36b2"] = "Shush! What\'s that sound... Hmm, seems, nah seems OK.", 
["addation_6d34b2021eac073c"] = "If you missed any info, just use the button to play a pre-recorded message.", 
["addation_f775c1d6cda2f56c"] = "This is our last chance to help The Elephant get his man to office. So get to work, gang.", 
["addation_0ad49bb82d6463b3"] = "Good job. Ernesto Sosa is dead. My point has been made.", 
["addation_1878a3a93f00d876"] = "Fuck it, you\'re here ain\'t you?", 
["addation_6d7563b1095c0708"] = "Get that C4 into the vault. And stand back!", 
["addation_6a4ecd679158d84b"] = "Now find a terminal in IT with internet access. Upload that data to me.", 
["addation_8e08ef4d92d7e4e1"] = "Confirmed! I\'m coming in at dock nine!", 
["addation_2ba1fffc8ef3c503"] = "The arena has a huge security floor run by Gensec. Part exhibition for corporate VIP\'s, but still a working vault. Tonight, we hit it. We got an Inside Man on this one. He stashed some C4 around the Arena. Gather it, blow the vault from beneath and get that sweet dirty money out. We\'re going to have some unexpected help on this one. You guys hear of a DJ called Alesso? Tonight\'s the last night of his East Coast tour, and he\'s promised to lift the roof. What better cover could you want?", 
["addation_3cc9c95d0c85323d"] = "There\'s one of \'em!", 
["addation_8543a6d712ae9e08"] = "Have a look around for anything useful while I see what we can do about this.", 
["addation_d9c2ef577b05d7ad"] = "The Beast is at work. ", 
["addation_365cb9b2d094a5e8"] = "This war need guns to keep going,  and now FBI have what is mine. Money is gone but hardware still at airport. Go and get the (fucking) weapon crates back.", 
["addation_92811bddeb13d5f3"] = "What the hell!? It\'s the cops!", 
["addation_f2b2359340b28abd"] = "Crap, heavy reinforcements moving in. You guys better jump in with the loot if you wanna get out of here.", 
["addation_459e261fc48bf3ee"] = "Very good.", 
["addation_039bed79d7883049"] = "Industrial, high-pressure water pump used by nearby timber mill. If we\'re lucky, and the right wagon lands near it, we can use it to fill the vault.", 
["addation_eef60c78d9024bf6"] = "You gotta go to the library!", 
["addation_ae69ab9e3f125478"] = "Okay, I got what I came for! Get me back to the truck so I can put the shit together.", 
["addation_d09de95c85c4a026"] = "These sons of bitches get nothing!", 
["addation_6e1ef82cc7343198"] = "I know you want to get out there and start working, but I have to make sure you know the drill. Times change, new equipment, new toys. I just want to make sure you got it all in check.", 
["addation_2f3babdab6284f60"] = "Zup, homes?", 
["addation_be212d959aef8f3b"] = "I\'m almost there, get ready!", 
["addation_cca26fc3e2b9d700"] = "There are millions of crates in there. Yes, millions. you just gotta find the right one. Use a terminal in the IT lab.", 
["addation_db45a6a11dd2c86b"] = "Ohhhh shhhheeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeiiiiiiiiit. Out-fuckin\'-standin\'!", 
["addation_113276969ed9f3da"] = "... go through with the trade now, as we agreed on!", 
["addation_73b10be183c2af2d"] = "They\'re going to hit you with snipers!", 
["addation_0449e3462f923e09"] = "I wish we had some goddamn equipment that worked... Start it again.", 
["addation_60bc00a0dda280a7"] = "They pulled the power, get it back on!", 
["addation_6835e68da60c1a31"] = "Okay, the data is being transferred to the server in the other room. You can either go and get it or stay and scan more bodies. I\'m sure Jimmy can find use for it and that means more cash for us.", 
["addation_93ad2203ac91ae8e"] = "Get some fake sentry guns up and running. It\'ll buy us some time and keep people in place.", 
["addation_cb23978b6e113605"] = "Another vault. Didn\'t expect that.", 
["addation_1176637f69070ac9"] = "That\'s them! They were here just like Wick said. Tie them up and leave them by the van. Wick will take care of the scum when we get back. ", 
["addation_ac8ce1e5218df67a"] = "Not going to miss that prison food, I can tell ya. Shit on a fuckin\' shingle.", 
["addation_d54750ff717a0d50"] = "Be there in a few minutes. Stand by.", 
["addation_f8e10baaaeda3033"] = "Time for a nice, old fashioned cookout, for sure!", 
["addation_ecd49851020c2773"] = "Nice. That\'s the keycard for the railcars. ", 
["addation_3d9cd018e8fa4cd3"] = "Ah, bravo! We\'re fueled and ready to go. Please, make your way aboard and let us get out of here. This was a fine day.", 
["addation_f3be564abd017352"] = "Just one more keycard. Gotta be around here somewhere.", 
["addation_cb3bb410db6dfe00"] = "Get those bags here!", 
["addation_2ae81291ea2bd8b6"] = "Make sure he\'s still breathing!", 
["addation_25a55a2330bb8b39"] = "Kill \'em all!", 
["addation_a91317fe89af6c94"] = "You need to take care of those Murkys!", 
["addation_64aebf2ac79b3fc0"] = "If you did it right, it will now cook!", 
["addation_40723891ecde912d"] = "Stop throwing the coke into the fucking water!", 
["addation_72dc06ce721364a3"] = "They\'re inside!", 
["addation_faeec9b773eb3512"] = "That\'ll surely bring the feds. Gotta think of a way to get the goats out of here.", 
