["addation_c293b4c5ea4a7792"] = "Everyone\'s here, good. The villa\'s on the other side of the airstrip. Sneak in there, find the lab. when you\'ve found the engine,  hustle it back to this airfield and wait for pick-up.", 
["addation_40bac11ee2d971a0"] = "I need eleven more, at least.", 
