["addation_ef7d3dda6879c7ea"] = "Screw the winch down!", 
["addation_3451264c10da6f49"] = "We can settle for this, let\'s go...", 
["addation_1541420efd1cad80"] = "It\'s ugly business, but it\'s gotta be done.", 
["addation_a56229133a9a4ccb"] = "Tear gas incoming! Stay clear and wait for it to die down.", 
["addation_c039bf2e570e1485"] = "They\'re on to us like a fucking sticker!", 
["addation_68e49e149847d3f0"] = "And when I cashed out, every other asshole did the same thing. But I was smart. First outta the gate, you know. Made a million bucks in a flash.", 
["addation_94e786053900ebca"] = "...muriatic acid?", 
["addation_1f9cceaa7d41a452"] = "You think I don\'t know what\'s goin on?...", 
["addation_ed125e69c7fb626a"] = "I will hold you to that, you chop!", 
["addation_65aaefcb8adbaace"] = "A new account. We can get that sorted right away.", 
