["addation_71fbd575f0ed6333"] = "Guys, it feels like something\'s in the air... Money!", 
["addation_aeef81b3b143c05f"] = "The Harvest & Trustee is a vulnerable bank so I see an opportunity for us. Case it so you can find out where. You\'re going to need to get into the vault using a thermal drill, get whatever\'s in there bagged up and moved back to the escape car. Use your judgment and don\'t be greedy... Good luck, folks.", 
