["addation_69e06c934b5321a9"] = "I bet Vlad gets his money tomorrow. Ha.", 
["addation_0616a58c5cf47b2b"] = "Keep at it.", 
["addation_e2aed13da239d347"] = "What are you doing here!?", 
["addation_124533f4ca759abd"] = "Blerrie! Murkywater operatives are trying to block off the area, keep away from them, yeah?", 
["addation_d399349cea5061ab"] = "Hey boss. There\'s some woman here, says she has some important information for you.", 
["addation_43369c469adf0b22"] = "Ok, listen up. To get inside that vault you need to get by the security system. Intel says that Garnet\'s son Ralph has the key card for it, but he also happens to be the birthday boy so that could be a problem. There\'s also a three-part security code split up onto different laptops because someone told \'em it would be safer. It\'d be great if you could get your hands on both the key card and code without raising any alarms, maybe pull a silent fast one on Mr. Garnet.", 
["addation_10b2e55249c22a18"] = "That\'s the door, but don\'t open it yet. We need to disable the alarm, hold on a second...", 
["addation_a6b45df1702e1add"] = "Roger. One moment please. Today\'s code is 8394. Please remember it next time. This is very sensitive information.", 
["addation_23dab256b0dfd6b0"] = "Okay, the alarm has kicked in a secondary lock on the gate - a magnetic seal. You need a terminal to release that. Let me find one.", 
["addation_a2e8114451fd511a"] = "Get that weapon charged, friends.", 
["addation_3866af38503c32e5"] = "They say having family is beautiful but sometimes I don\'t know. Now find that stupid fuck and free him - hopefully he\'s not too drunk to remember in which boxes he hid the cocaine.", 
["addation_b3ecef1cafc2bd65"] = "Careful though, don\'t get discovered.", 
["addation_e4a8623359eac657"] = "The vault\'s open and ready for you, gang. Just grab that loot.", 
["addation_d3970f9702ae1003"] = "Sweet that is some good old loot...", 
["addation_954a851dc2ef2816"] = "Damn it! Plan B, just find that server room!", 
["addation_9ba9cbbf99387aaa"] = "There\'s not much left now... If you just hurry up you might make a few extra grand.", 
["addation_e51e4372361e9975"] = "You gotta help Charon! Clear the street!", 
["addation_872f62d940b5be43"] = "Sounds like the cops are about to bust through to Wilson\'s house!", 
["addation_eca49d1ad5b3aee7"] = "If your guy Locke doesn\'t come through, Cabot will sort it out.", 
["addation_91dccac75211c32a"] = "Throw it if you have to, just move it fast!", 
["addation_e94ed4996e7aec67"] = "That\'s it! Great job, gang.", 
