["addation_a45f1fe74cc4c390"] = "My guess is the code is in someone\'s email. Find an FBI terminal and gain access.", 
["addation_819acd0fd38f4930"] = "Prolonged exposure can kill, so you gotta decide if you want to risk going in now or wait it out.", 
["addation_612fd7cf98de3336"] = "It\'s nothing my crew can\'t handle, yeah?", 
["addation_a26087f7cf8d9f05"] = "...Might be able to hack them with bank computers, yeah?", 
["addation_13789eb04a4de2d9"] = "Power\'s down. Look for the circuit box and get it back on.", 
["addation_d284ea3a245a2de3"] = "This is good security. A code and a retinal scanner.", 
