["addation_95dcba70f79684dc"] = "Are you having trouble getting the Beast to run?", 
["addation_9c8b87e50811adb5"] = "Woah! Wherever Commissar is, he heard that!", 
["addation_c4d3b2706f18e064"] = "Shit! Po po is here!", 
["addation_919fa0bedbdde2b5"] = "Close. So close.", 
["addation_c0dae5df07d2ae13"] = "Some nice stuff in those cases. Some knock-offs too. If you\'re going to snatch it, snatch the real stuff - look for cases with alarms. I\'m sure a clever crew like you can figure it out.", 
