["addation_afa3453ea4c8ed15"] = "Well, our explosives guy delivered. Two transports have stopped. Get to work!", 
["addation_04da18c6d06b4c7a"] = "Crew, this is us ending Mendoza ops in DC right here and right now. Hit that bus hard and take their money. Hector just wants these clowns ended so the money is ours. Set down in 3, 2, 1, go!", 
