["addation_6943ea0ac611c8c2"] = "Now hurry up friends, get in there and find the thing we came here for. Garrett probably has it in a safe or something.", 
["addation_41a263d09940edc5"] = "Find more gas and pour it on the fire. Keep it burning! Fry him!", 
