["addation_c9974b6e8ade46cb"] = "This place looks like it hasn\'t been decorated since the 60\'s.", 
["addation_cd04da6ac0adfbef"] = "Dammit... This is bad...", 
["addation_77ec7bad7450c8cf"] = "The streets are crawling with cops! Not getting out that way. Light a flare and I\'ll bring in a chopper.", 
["addation_45c67e43f1ad4c73"] = "There\'s our guy. He\'s shit faced! Get him away from there. There\'s a deserted lumber yard near your position.", 
["addation_cf7dfba870130275"] = "Alright, that\'s his office. Now we move to the next stage.", 
["addation_f4dd7a26a1563ea6"] = "OK, loaded!", 
["addation_d35979905ecc6dd4"] = "What the fuck is this!?", 
["addation_982891a134003644"] = "Through the hole, gang! You\'re getting out of there!", 
["addation_63a800ca01e50f2e"] = "I can arrange for extra ammunition to be left.", 
["addation_4c2555aed51d57b1"] = "Wait.. what... they\'ve got additional security blocks. You gotta disable them. Find a security switchboard and rewire the system.", 
["addation_91532d20a7a84746"] = "Well, lads, thanks for breakin\' me out. But I shouldn\'t have been there to begin with. Someone set me up. I\'m sure of it. The Feds had too much on me. Way more than those mingebag wankers could dig up. Someone ratted. Someone fucked me. And I\'m gonna find out who.$NL;$NL;Now, it ain\'t gonna be easy. No fannying about around the edges, right? No shadowy deals or contacts, or that bollocks. We\'re going to the source. The biggest FBI nest. Gonna find out who screwed me.", 
["addation_0774f46e97383ef2"] = "Hurry up, they\'re wasting thousands of dollars worth of coke every damn second!", 
["addation_e0656ae17fdb8abb"] = "You gotta restart the override.", 
["addation_525cf9be5209d437"] = "Eh, I\'ll say it for you: you didn\'t come here only to save me, now did ya? No, you\'re here for the custom built bike, am I right or am I right? I\'ll help you. I owe you that much, but you\'ll have to get me the parts I need.", 
["addation_0eeed1b1c765eb0b"] = "That safe path won\'t last forever, gang. Make sure you make the most of it. You can create it again, though.", 
["addation_bffe7eb1d0c178f6"] = "Shit!", 
["addation_543f88e7f3d9beac"] = "Oh, a J\xc3\xa4ger Mark II... difficult things to get through without destroying the contents.", 
["addation_513bcb18f5ae4093"] = "Guys! You got one minute!", 
["addation_6b1c7c11dddf9c83"] = "BFD needs power - lots of it! Hook her up to a couple of sockets. They\'re located inside the casino. Don\'t let them get disconnected.", 
["addation_d40da2e0fc352398"] = "It\'s procedure. Who am I talking to again?", 
["addation_d068051de1cdd99e"] = "OK. The panic room door is controlled with two keycards and a retinal scanner. No problem.", 
["addation_d732f39076ad9ddf"] = "Don\'t get stuck anywhere, keep moving up! It\'ll be worth it, but it\'s wasting away quickly!", 
["addation_c0f76d1c41af38c3"] = "Jesus, Bain. Like I would have forgotten how to get past a fucking fence? Anyhow, I\'m through now.", 
["addation_2aee639b5d818992"] = " Yes, Duke lent me a book. But exactly why are these things so important, aside from their considerable monetary value?", 
["addation_a55e22812429ffc8"] = "Fantastic! No time to lose, though. Fire it up and get felling those trees.", 
["addation_59a206ecca52c3a2"] = "Those shutters will not be able to withstand thermite. Get some on there!", 
["addation_8f855e65429cf201"] = "Soviet era machinery. Slow. So slow.", 
["addation_0156fda6427a972e"] = "Hurry man, my ass is gonna be grass like if the cops had lawn-mowers!", 
["addation_fb5f930b048d0a24"] = "Good choice, gang. It\'s all about the payday when it comes down to it. You know the drill, keep scanning them bodies for more data.", 
["addation_d6fc8b8aa31ae9f6"] = "This will distract the guards in a way I\'m sure you will find very useful.", 
["addation_c566c0e58a2aa7c3"] = "Fuck yeah. This is mine.", 
["addation_12545e548dd39515"] = "The market for these cars demands they are in perfect condition. Keep it quiet, and you\'ll keep the cops away. Which means no bullet holes.", 
["addation_fb1c3e06ee34bb4a"] = "Yes sir, we\'ll help you with that right away.", 
["addation_60173790ca99d8eb"] = "That takes care of the safe. Now you can open it up!", 
["addation_4f0dbff0ade168a0"] = "You can go get more C4 outside if you need it, yeah?", 
["addation_e583d88eb120291c"] = "OK guys, get into the bank and find the vault and drill it open. Make sure no one triggers the alarm or escapes.", 
["addation_bb9e1113647d6c1d"] = "Hey, culeros! You fucked with the wrong gang!", 
["addation_18a9b2eb84b67080"] = "The Commissar is bunkered down somewhere around Foggy Bottom. Find a clue for that place.", 
["addation_e9528251ccfe1cb2"] = "There you go, better get those stones to Mr Blonde. His boss will be able to move them.", 
["addation_06b82b49b40e5c31"] = "You\'re not going to just stroll out the front. Get upstairs, and blast through into the office next door. That\'s the way out.", 
