["addation_eaf42e2bd3d712a0"] = "Dear friends, this is going to be a tough one. The Kataru have stepped up their pursuit of Bain\'s dinges, and we\'ve got to take away their toys, yeah? The warehouse we\'re going to hit is the most important Murky site there is, and they\'re working on some very strange projects. They only let me near the place once, and I didn\'t see much, so we can\'t know what to expect. I\'ve pulled in every last favor with my remaining contacts at Murky, and have got us a way in, but we\'re going in blind. Once we do this, there will be no going back. We\'re essentially proclaiming open war on Murky, but we owe the bliksems for Bain. There\'s going to be a caliber of security we haven\'t seen before, so don\'t get NAAFI once you\'re in, yeah?", 
