["addation_935104fa484455d7"] = "And I had this guy come up, you know, wanted to buy the whole thing but I said, you know, it\'s just money and it\'s not me.. you know?", 
["addation_e337abe0e1f23e54"] = "Ever since I was a little kid, I always wanted to be a player, you know.", 
["addation_9bcf0c87e1c23d2d"] = "Listen, you know, getting paid to do something you love...it\'s a dream, man.", 
["addation_14d11ce5183f173b"] = "All this ass around here. You know how much that is? But they worth it. I mean, they can dance. And by dance...", 
["addation_77018b3b46e1243a"] = "It\'s Mitchell. Mitchell! Mitch.....ell. Now let me hear ya say it.", 
["addation_8e5a3e34803f3f6c"] = "Out-fucking-standing.", 
["addation_b36e5537a57644ad"] = "King was the top dog, the big kahoona, the.....the fucking king, man!", 
["addation_d97ea43046a06df9"] = "Come with me.", 
["addation_ed4210dd5d31d71e"] = "I\'ll show you the leak.", 
["addation_b7a40d13887180dd"] = "This is a ten thousand dollar carpet man! Fix it!", 
["addation_b89a1534435860d0"] = "Okay you got me, you got me good!", 
["addation_9f1796cf3c65a3fb"] = "I had a bad feeling about these guys.", 
["addation_5efa7f3842a6d0ae"] = "What gave us away?", 
["addation_debe2368aba96863"] = "(laughs shortly, manically)", 
["addation_e55dee5ab039f7b0"] = "If you\'re not gonna talk, I\'m just gonna go ahead and shoot you.", 
["addation_33ca7a7834b08838"] = "And here I was, being all polite. What say I feed you some lead?", 
["addation_0808071352a8388c"] = "It\'s way out there, behind the parking lot. The door to the unit is pretty thick and I don\'t have the key. We\'ll need to cut it open. Should be a saw around here.", 
["addation_41d7a85e401feaf3"] = "So, here\'s some good news and bad news. Bad news is my car died. Good news is that I had time to grab some diamonds from the trunk. They\'re in a storage unit nearby.", 
["addation_4fcfe691a5381b9f"] = "Great, at least this fiasco isn\'t a total loss.", 
["addation_a2a0c71ebcd29547"] = "Hey, I just got word. Cabot\'s got a guy comin\' to pick us up but you guys better split before he gets here. He ain\'t too happy right now.", 
["addation_26d13ac8901faf71"] = "Hey. Almost thought you guys got lost or somethin\'.", 
["addation_283bee8ece6afd7f"] = "Cabot\'s gonna go nuts when he hears about this.", 
["addation_e6e5b963856adfe6"] = "Hey, crooks don\'t slide on hoods. Only cops.", 
["addation_c858da5251201ed5"] = "Nine down.", 
["addation_fab0d13769f87092"] = " This should buy a nice retirement fund.", 
["addation_7a2be51b41012f6e"] = "Yeah, about that. It\'s out here. In my car.", 
["addation_02112f02f009258c"] = "What\'s takin\' so long, Goddamnit?", 
["addation_c2b0552e1540d453"] = "*grunts, wheezes*", 
["addation_d8f2d808ada9a525"] = "Some weird shit happening on this job.", 
["addation_77a1796deb338b9d"] = "Ain\'t never seen a job this screwed.", 
["addation_e98e8b676fbdaaad"] = "Hey guys, it\'s been.. interesting.", 
["addation_a7936097d6565e29"] = "Goddamn cops!", 
["addation_b15eea9fffe7e21c"] = "Meet our promoted Cloakers! I\'m sure you\'ll love their cuffs...", 
["addation_d4be0dfe53534986"] = "We are prepared to renegotiate the hostage release and have been authorized to make a higher offer!", 
["addation_36455d9a340cd15d"] = "You asked for it, creeps. Dead or alive, you\'re coming with us.", 
["addation_766ac85b1684bd16"] = "We\'re got the asset secure. That\'s game over for the perps, over.", 
["addation_c877240be1c1f9d6"] = "Right!", 
["addation_a102c379b258c9f5"] = "Ah thank you. And may I say, you two are the finest dressed nurses in the whole hospital.", 
["addation_d973318f4f1de25a"] = "You\'re breaking up... Can you hear me ok?", 
["addation_615a68e4e14c7c17"] = "Why does it feel like I shouldn\'t be here right now?", 
["addation_aa2f44efd5e91a62"] = "Nice and easy guys. This one is important.", 
["addation_ac34d85c79bf50cc"] = "So, might any individual in this here room at present, be able to present to me, a constitutional provision regarding treasonous acts against the United States? Anyone? Well, Section 3, article 3 of the Constitution provides "Treason against the United States, shall consist only in levying war against them, or in adhering to their enemies, giving them aid and comfort. No person shall be convicted of Treason unless on the Testimony of two Witnesses to the same overt Act, or on...?....on...? Would anyone care to finish? Anyone?... Bueller?", 
["addation_0dda5a40ac4058cd"] = "Copy that. Let me pull it up...it\'s 8394. Don\'t let it get out.", 
["addation_ef45d46d9e294228"] = "OK, throw me the paintings and you\'ll get your money!", 
["addation_cbe45082cf1bdf03"] = "Come on, we need more than that!", 
["addation_a4c947306bd0ef28"] = "Come on already! We need more bags!", 
["addation_2be70a3be821d18d"] = "Oh shit! This wasn\'t the deal! We are outta here!", 
["addation_b0e41548c1452e2d"] = "You better hurry up and fix that leakage.", 
["addation_4dcd566d6b2e933b"] = "*mumbles*", 
["addation_ede593e3078b5f4a"] = "Nice work. The C4 will alert the crowd unless we time it with Alesso\'s pyrotechnics. Head upstairs and patch me into the tech booth.", 
["addation_46b10c08e60674e3"] = "That was intense! All right, head back to the vault and let\'s finish the job. ", 
["addation_d9d7e58ec96f5138"] = "I\'m sending Bile your way!", 
["addation_ebf73b4efbd4a030"] = "Ok, nice and easy. Just get those masks off, blend in with the crowd and we won\'t have any issues. The van will be waiting for you.", 
["addation_8ab75b800489dff7"] = "The cops have this place surrounded. We\'re going to have to "gracefully improvise".", 
["addation_e57beae85c304c3e"] = "Cops are closing in on the arena. Stay on your toes, this will get hairy.", 
["addation_959de17471b536e2"] = "Another door. Watch the guards and cameras, gang...", 
["addation_c8af3e645d006ca8"] = "Another closet. Great. That lock won\'t give you problems.", 
["addation_ff429bdc85465499"] = "And there is the final closet.", 
["addation_d93a1d3726ae9fba"] = "More C4. Not quite enough. Find the last batch. Keep searching.", 
["addation_4795069f0601f883"] = "Don\'t forget - the garage is where you need to plant the C4.", 
["addation_d86444fc2ec6ded1"] = "You need to be at the pyro booth. It\'s on the top floor - get there!", 
["addation_1e17f9bdc1c575eb"] = "Haul ass to the pyro booth, guys. Top floor.", 
["addation_05f75bffa7cc3c2e"] = "Look at the crowd. Insane. Right, focus on the job, and let\'s give them a show.", 
["addation_e18041a85f5e3576"] = "I\'m grabbing the pyro schedule. I\'ll guide you guys through, and time it with the C4.", 
["addation_efbfa3164cd26487"] = "Okay... left button!", 
["addation_96b50dd8f105c70e"] = "Center button!", 
["addation_90725040c909c834"] = "Middle and right.", 
["addation_955208477366bc94"] = "Come on, guys. You have to get the cutters onto the vault floor.", 
["addation_cda1b48ed5648cb7"] = "That chute there can transport the loot to the back rooms of...", 
["addation_582df615981acb29"] = "Don\'t forget - stow that loot up into one of the vents.", 
["addation_2183442b3f58d955"] = "Guys. Answer that intercom when you\'re ready to bail. Whatever you leave behind, stays behind.", 
["addation_9cdc4f847c34d555"] = "It was loud and got attention. Excellent work. Tough for Gensec though. Their new design is a joke.", 
["addation_b8dbf88579549845"] = "Good find. But you\'ll need more C4. Keep searching.", 
["addation_3d577aefda49de80"] = "I got Vlad on the line.", 
["addation_76b5880bb2c1eb49"] = "Vlad\'s pretty upset about these safes. Wants to talk to you.", 
["addation_1b10d440668fb468"] = "You heard the man. Let\'s find those trucks.", 
["addation_40a71eb76616a083"] = "Great. Now crack those trucks open. Let\'s see what Vlad was shipping.", 
["addation_e4a6224bc1a3f9ae"] = "Well, at least it isn\'t nukes this time.", 
["addation_d6d98a5f386c641c"] = "Come on, crew. Get the safes out. Put your back into it.", 
["addation_ec0dcc89912dadb6"] = "Telling the pilot to return with the C4 to bust you through there. Just hang in there.", 
["addation_4307a09d3569e6c8"] = "All right. Safes are in. We\'re getting out through the yard. Make sure the truck is there!", 
["addation_aebab2bcda3ae5fe"] = "Gang, the pilot can\'t see you. You need to light that flare.", 
["addation_f224deffb1734d27"] = "And....lift off! Outstanding work, crew!", 
["addation_7db1725cf07384b2"] = "Guys, the wreckage is incredible. Rubble blocking everything.", 
["addation_47909a30399185c4"] = "The trucks are here somewhere. Vlad\'s guys will be too, so watch your fire.", 
["addation_ddd48c3499e75de9"] = "Got it! Construction yard, with a truck. Looks like the best way out of here, but you\'ll need C4 to bust that wall. Sending it now. Mind the safes!", 
["addation_e355fd1dd1262249"] = "Gang, there\'s a construction yard across the river! Got a truck parked up. Reckon it\'s our best way out. Sending you C4 now. Protect the safes!", 
["addation_e0ea19b2c92c2da8"] = "That truck looks perfect. Now get the safes loaded on board - all of them.", 
["addation_3017c1889e5565e4"] = "Get the safes loaded onto that truck!", 
["addation_01895e8fe607088b"] = "We\'re using a magnetic crane to drop a little present in the path of the Gensec convoy - a steel container of professional badasses. Hit the trucks, and get the loot to the getaway. These docks have a rich history of heistery, gentlemen - do it proud.", 
["addation_0912d759c031d9e9"] = "We have a stolen ambulance all ready to set up a roadblock, and a Gensec convoy en-route from Dulles. It\'s an old trick, but a classic. Get whatever\'s in the trucks to your escape driver. We\'re deep in Indian country here, gentlemen, so expect a fast response from D.C.\'s finest.", 
["addation_1cc365c984760074"] = "I\'m sure you guys have tangled with Gensec before. They\'re the East Coast\'s premier provider of security solutions, if you believe their brochure. But, PR aside, these guys are serious. Today, we hit them.", 
["addation_479aeb011cde5da7"] = "Great job. I\'ll get my contacts fencing the shinies. And see what I can find out about that blueprint. Stay tuned.", 
["addation_17c3abb706344605"] = "Haha! You did it! This jewelry should be worth a few bucks don\'t you think?", 
["addation_ff89cc4f1e3c2c8c"] = "Great job gentlemen!", 
["addation_e7ff82756f6e73ae"] = "Hurry! Cops are already on their way!", 
["addation_1fcb305ccba5fdd7"] = "Good job, now get the bags to the van so we can get the hell out of here!", 
["addation_270b56ba1d57ceac"] = "I\'m sending the helicopter, keep bagging the stuff!", 
["addation_a48592a4772d9129"] = "The Gensec trucks just turned into our guy\'s sight. Wait for it... Wait for it...", 
["addation_99aace795a8c8612"] = "The target is spotted. Just need to get you into position and...", 
["addation_657066df6b26d2f4"] = "OK, Gensec is approaching. Gun that engine. Move! Move!", 
["addation_05adab64e8699eed"] = "That\'s a Royal Flush, gang. Every God damn truck is ready for the picking. Get to work!", 
["addation_87fe2a5f7b393f84"] = "Must be that drivers first day. The dumbass stopped for the ambulance! Now it\'s your turn, gang. Get out there and do your job!", 
["addation_8a1f0fc7f592ecce"] = "They fell for it. Three transports. Crews are on the street, trying to figure out what\'s happening. Hit them hard!", 
["addation_d3575a6339544659"] = "It\'s a beautiful building, but we\'re bringing ugly business. We\'ll need codes to get deeper in, so look for their servers.", 
["addation_cd6c9a8a96ae53e1"] = "Hook me up. I should be able to get into their system from here. ", 
["addation_e24a01dfe16c7542"] = "Patch me in. I can do some mischief from here.", 
["addation_c0ae835306b512f3"] = "That was the wrong computer. Try another one. Maybe there\'s a way to figure out which terminal we need.", 
["addation_bd4116257b14ead9"] = "The alarm shut down the time lock. Stay cool. There\'s a maintenance office on the roof. Get there. We should be able to rewire it.", 
["addation_83928944a80cddc6"] = "Rewire those circuits. That should reset the time lock.", 
["addation_7f288527558fa60c"] = "While we wait for that, and if you\'ve got the stones, get to the roof and get the zip-line set up.", 
["addation_eed962e5d00dfc55"] = "The cops messed up the time lock! Get it going again!", 
["addation_60bfe850d45aa702"] = "Quite the view, huh? Well, I\'ve got something else to show you. Get to the control booth.", 
["addation_8e5b375a02944f43"] = "Even diamond bits break! You\'re gonna need the spare parts to get it going again.", 
["addation_0a3f36a474347e54"] = "Vault\'s breached! Now, let\'s see what Benevolent has.", 
["addation_4ecb61d727512da6"] = "Great. Now place that C4 and we can start getting out of this place.", 
["addation_dabc599d1e0fd7a6"] = "Bile\'s on-site, gang. Start getting the bags to him.", 
["addation_c3fcccec974ffd09"] = "The elevator shaft is open. That\'s the path to the van. Start hauling.", 
["addation_baa0c14fde85ca38"] = "Someone answer the phone!", 
["addation_e8ec89dc223d39dd"] = "One down, one to go.", 
["addation_7036c806a06d6e99"] = "Great. Now the last step. Find the managers code. It should be on his computer.", 
["addation_bc3d1d59a38431f9"] = "Time to light it up, guys.", 
["addation_c0464c7cf9c4268c"] = "Aluminum and iron oxide... Beautiful.", 
["addation_2c09bfa4b12fded1"] = "Guys, the elevators are moving. Expect heat from there.", 
["addation_2db6d654bcc7dd8c"] = "This is a historic day, gang. Haha, you finally cracked the Benevolent.", 
["addation_dc5e9877ebed8bbd"] = "You just ensured yourselves a place in the history books, gang. Simply outstanding!", 
["addation_cb0bf0ad2e8792f8"] = "Those pictures might help us later.", 
["addation_285f8e477c309a64"] = "OK we got the address - he lives in a high security villa, up in the mountains, real secluded, luxurious area. We will be going in blind with no intel. Arm yourself and let\'s go. ", 
["addation_f602a92b60cde94d"] = "Anyway get close, hit \'em hard, find the safe, and get whatever intel you can find there. Take all of it.", 
["addation_42956f500df55653"] = "I\'m in, this might take a few...", 
["addation_4e0d708d6a649a27"] = "Damn it! They\'ve turned of the power to the server! Get it back up!", 
["addation_cd2171103149af01"] = "OK, I\'m coming in, get the server ready!", 
["addation_2b48c843f497e2e9"] = "This one seems to be malfunctioning, I\'ll be back to pick up another one.", 
["addation_91ad0a29b46b59bb"] = "They\'ve deployed snipers. Stay low.", 
["addation_1d1e0d9e912af8fa"] = "Good work people. That was a hell of a thing to move, but it\'s the right engine and it\'s locked up tight. Maybe one day we\'ll go freelancing and take it back, huh?", 
["addation_adb5c03aac36bed0"] = "Bull\'s-eye. Point Break-down: get inside the house, find the lab, get the engine, get back to this airfield, escape. Good luck.", 
