["addation_be04a9fc00192c36"] = "I mean they don\'t need it that bad... So let\'s hit that vault.", 
["addation_4d70c1e580c0f814"] = "Today\'s our lucky day - cash delivery from the airport to this bank, all sorts of denominations... So I propose we do a little money exchange of our own. ", 
["addation_720045c944cebbb9"] = "Looks like the local Trustee bank had someone renting a whole lot of safe deposit boxes. Now I don\'t know what\'s in them, and don\'t ask how I know, but I think this is a bank job we can\'t miss.", 
["addation_74853639c393f23a"] = "OK, standard bank hit, only we\'re going for the gold drop off day. Gotta remain liquid, right?", 
["addation_f1bfa1713672cf01"] = "People I think this job is a gold mine. Almost literally. ", 
["addation_d9f670b0d5fac29e"] = "OK, You\'re gonna need a thermal drill for this gig. My guy stashed it around the back of the bank. Get it and get to work on the vault.  Keep in mind there\'s security cameras and lots of civilians. Go win the gold, folks.", 
["addation_83787707c1e71967"] = "The Harvest & Trustee is a medium-size branch bank, vault in the back, a few different entries. Case the place first... You\'re going to want to get into the vault, drill it, get whatever\'s inside out of there and back to the escape car.", 
