["addation_92ec170cf4127a7e"] = "It\'s open! Bag the gold!", 
["addation_d3a9fb93475c85e6"] = "Nice. Now start her up.", 
["addation_9c6648a45cbb63cf"] = "That was one good heist. I owe you all a round at the Tasteful club. See you this evening guys.", 
["addation_50b4a72133eef76e"] = "Loot bags in place and money ready to get divided. You guys never disappoint. Love it!", 
["addation_6704c65fbb897413"] = "I don\'t say superb often, but I\'m saying it now. Good work.", 
["addation_db7cc2a7775ff047"] = "If there were more crews like you I think the world would need to store its valuables elsewhere.", 
["addation_c2eb04b6aaec714d"] = "...The plan breaks down like this.", 
["addation_3a3bb04f553bc2de"] = "...Situation looks this way.", 
["addation_be64d68c97b9f0d9"] = "...This is how it looks.", 
["addation_60d9f66f92f58342"] = "...This is how it looks right now.", 
["addation_df2cfc6f631d5c0e"] = "That could have gone a lot worse. Now untie him and let\'s get going.", 
["addation_49ed64d1beafab16"] = "The mechanic said he wants you to bring him some kind of special tools from the workshop. Hurry up.", 
["addation_af773b38d503a51e"] = "The workshop is where you\'ll find the tools. That\'s what the mechanic said.", 
["addation_809862e08f784698"] = "Rust\'s bike isn\'t going to roll without an engine, and the mechanic said to check inside the clubhouse. Get a move on.", 
["addation_ee0be5ba21f6f674"] = "The mechanic mentioned he saw them store engines inside the clubhouse. Go have a look.", 
["addation_daa9a865885f7601"] = "A gas tank and exhaust pipes, gang. That\'s what the mechanic said he needed, and you\'ll find them in the workshop.", 
["addation_adf0e986e29c4b3f"] = "Great, that\'s the part he needed.", 
["addation_420e2006b373ab3d"] = "There\'s the escape! Ride through the gate and you\'ll be safe!", 
["addation_a78028e12ad6fd24"] = "Ride through the gate and you\'ll be safe!", 
["addation_5bf5891e02efa7c6"] = "I guess the man really wanted a soda...", 
["addation_2ad9f02ce06b56de"] = "Now, we gotta find out what room shares a vent with the security center. We\'ll use it to knock out the guards. First, get building blueprints. They should be inside the archives.", 
["addation_a65868a3896175c3"] = "101!", 
["addation_29dd67426dcf8d39"] = "Screw the alarms, guys. Just grab The Dentists\' loot and we can be done.", 
["addation_01fd82df714ce718"] = "The code has three numbers, each color coded. You\'ll find them in computer briefcases.", 
["addation_eb4650e4840097d1"] = "Good job, we already have that code. Use it on the armory.", 
["addation_840da99f18514c63"] = "Don\'t forget to grab C4 from the armory.", 
["addation_18bb3a0cf1a29d83"] = "You bet on the right spot! There\'s the vault!", 
["addation_4fec9a361212b7cc"] = "Great. Now turn her back on.", 
["addation_7f46469a26a2edd9"] = "Looks like one of her coolant tanks is finished. Be gents and fetch that girl a refill. Uh, from the crapper.", 
["addation_88e47cde0bb3095a"] = "Watch out gang! BFD overheats if you don\'t give her enough water. Get it from the bathroom.", 
["addation_9eee2a16b8633380"] = "BFD needs cooling. Refill the tank with water Hurry!", 
["addation_f6df91184b3ad0d9"] = "Will one of you clowns just grab that loot, please?", 
["addation_330bc981e6535e1b"] = "All right, that\'s it! Throw it up onto BFD.", 
