["addation_7c80c358a68fc218"] = "Hot damn! You\'re on a hot streak!", 
["addation_0f602e669614cc1b"] = "How much did you win? Can we all retire?", 
["addation_0a3ea5db51f2a54f"] = "The reception area. Remember the location. Might come in handy.", 
["addation_ed38d4f5ff804071"] = "Exterior lounge. Nice for a cool drink..", 
["addation_d2157cb3cb565f67"] = "This game room is the heart of The Golden Grin.", 
["addation_55f5793191b37a39"] = "Get the blueprints in the archives. They\'re somewhere in the employee only areas..", 
["addation_bdcf25c5258166ee"] = "Where are those blueprints, gang? Scan \'em, send \'em. You can do it in IT.", 
["addation_9c7a1040af8947c9"] = "It shares a vent with the Security Center.", 
["addation_f714e66132ee2c38"] = "Let me check. Room...", 
["addation_ac383eb50f15d4bb"] = "Now, the vault is located down in the Security Center. You have to get down and through there to reach it.", 
["addation_9d62afe7644138ae"] = "This is... Gerd. I\'m calling you from The Golden Grin Customer Satisfaction Department.", 
["addation_cbfec6f80b2537a1"] = "We have some excellent lobster tails for you to enjoy.", 
["addation_7facd9ec4b2da207"] = "We got those little pastry balls with the chocolate and cream.", 
["addation_2d4f77ade712533d"] = "And if you want, we can even make you toast.", 
["addation_e58505ccae326370"] = "Grab those bags, gang, come on!", 
["addation_a00741af2cfc8179"] = "You need to hook BFD up with the winch.", 
["addation_e327b817e66cc3e9"] = "Looks like he\'s running dry. Bring him another with a little extra flavor in it. I\'m sure you can find a bottle in one of the bars and spike it.", 
["addation_965af8da5086fcd1"] = "Pinky Demon schnapps? Huh. Find it, spike it, serve it.", 
["addation_ce10aa7924eeb8e5"] = "Pick up that keycard, and get to his room.", 
["addation_d1e1f3f727efe24c"] = "That\'s the alarm. OK, gang. Plan B. Force our way through.", 
["addation_f40c79142979bd1d"] = "The alarm. All right. Time for Plan B. No mercy, crew.", 
["addation_7e36ca4d5a0f4302"] = "Look for the armory. Intel says they\'re holding C4. For "extraordinary cases". Well, this is one of those extraordinary cases.", 
["addation_411609a6552fab86"] = "Dentist tells me they have C4 in the armory there. Get there, and get it.", 
["addation_6cb7eb2688c99535"] = "That\'s the first number. Need two more.", 
["addation_bc638bf1c6a5da50"] = "Okay, that\'s the digits for the armory code. Enter it!", 
["addation_0a4d9ba95b9866a0"] = "Now just hold tight and wait for Bile to drop the winch.", 
["addation_f49344315ee4cc7d"] = "Put the winch together where I marked, crew.", 
["addation_bee7446500bd4d28"] = "All right, get those fireworks onto the terrace.", 
["addation_454d314ffc31d903"] = "Light the fireworks, and stand back.", 
["addation_e5a1b0bd61c388a1"] = "That damn barrier is preventing the drill from coming down. Get to security and open it.", 
["addation_5c60a8bcc10efcd9"] = "Get hacking those skylight controls and keep the damn cops off.", 
["addation_22c6b0a9f0536924"] = "Who the - damn cops messed with the hack. Restart it!", 
["addation_f614a77c5bd6dbf3"] = "You need to get BFD right above the vault. The winch will move her, so get them hooked up.", 
["addation_a9bf8c2d0c4c8657"] = "BFD is a greedy girl. Needs a lot of power. Hook her up to two sockets. You can find them inside the casino. And keep the cops off.", 
["addation_24efa4eaf7de42f7"] = "Damn, BFD  lost power. Damn cops... reconnect the sockets.", 
["addation_961310279c79db21"] = "Throw the BFD\'s switch! Let the show begin!", 
["addation_c928f6e664c35219"] = "Wait for BFD to crack through the vault. Even this monster will take time. Keep the cops away.", 
["addation_8adab6a37f0f03c6"] = "BFD broke down. Gonna need tools to repair it.", 
["addation_99434dd5317e0d08"] = "She\'s all done! Quickly, down into the vault!", 
["addation_8a43fc21abc36938"] = "Outstanding! Now, get in the limo and end this. Or grab more loot. Your choice.", 
["addation_2cd6d59dadb00fb4"] = "You got that USB yet? Surely IT will have one.", 
["addation_a1eebd0739fd9dbc"] = "I\'m guessing any decent IT department will have a spare USB.", 
["addation_bd9b81ac1e4fa5bc"] = "Great! He should be back gambling in no time. Wait for him to take a sip, let nature do its thing. When he dashes off to the crapper, follow him and get that card.", 
["addation_07e7ef58fea9e160"] = "All right. Now let\'s just wait for him to try that drink. He\'s going to run for the John any second. Follow him. Get his keycard.", 
["addation_2506721cd760900e"] = "Get him down! Tie him up!", 
["addation_f4b964b321811905"] = "First briefcase is held by the casino manager. Second by the Pit Boss. Lastly, look for the head of security.", 
["addation_56b0bfa42088165f"] = "First digit for the vault code. Keep searching. We need all three.", 
["addation_7b2993cf92d3ec42"] = "Good job, that\'s the second number found. Just one more.", 
["addation_85b65cc578910692"] = "Good work. We\'ll need these three digits for the vault once we\'re through the Security Center.", 
["addation_505b95acfc3f8762"] = "Nice. Security chief\'s number. He won\'t be happy to lose this.", 
["addation_ebc93fb1e34b1a50"] = "Outstanding, guys, we\'re in! Help yourselves, give nothing back. Remember, our goal is the Dentists\' loot.", 
["addation_19475a7c99743517"] = "You need to eliminate those thugs.", 
["addation_6ae966d53f3abdfb"] = "Don\'t forget to find the elves. Shout at them to make them work.", 
["addation_3b01dbc016998e78"] = "Straightforward job, this one. A bunch of thugs are running a little operation. Got a bunch of "elves" cutting coke that Vlad wants. Deal with the thugs, and then get the elves producing. Shouting at them should do it. Get as much coke as Vlad needs, and we\'re done.", 
["addation_d34f680915b115a4"] = "That electric box controls the gate. Sure you could have it open in seconds.", 
["addation_af2914943d745645"] = "The storage room guys. Get in there and get the car keys.", 
["addation_6645842134ee741f"] = "The storage room is your target. That\'s where we\'ll find the keys.", 
["addation_8a6254d7a23681b9"] = "Locked. Damn it! Alright, stay cool. Find the manager. Take him hostage. I\'m sure he can help us get in.", 
["addation_97ad991a58dd9ea0"] = "Find the manager. He\'s wearing a black suit, going bald. Tie him up and see if he can help.", 
["addation_d84d78275720e2bb"] = "Logged in. Alright, I\'ll have that lock open soon. Head back to the van and grab the C4. Might as well get the escape ready.", 
["addation_3cd08df7754e5e5f"] = "Guys, grab the C4 from the van. Get it on the street.", 
["addation_d88dc1f1e6f148a2"] = "Got it! I\'m in the system. While I finish this, get out to the van and grab the C4. Plant it in the street.", 
["addation_c124ca571aecd3e8"] = "OK, I\'ll set these off remotely. Now get back to the storage room. It\'s open!", 
["addation_58640b8183bdaa09"] = "The keys are in the storage room. Grab \'em!", 
["addation_e1085e3875df1961"] = "I\'m jealous you\'re going to get to drive this beast.", 
["addation_afc8ba1ee3ebe069"] = "Now the fun part - steal a car! I\'ll blast the road - take cover!", 
["addation_5f9ace150ff209f9"] = "Search the office! Get the guys name! Not much time.", 
["addation_160b4c889ad35c5c"] = "Check the manager\'s office. Look for the IT guys name. Come on, come on!", 
["addation_470890b890e9618e"] = "Now put the car in the container, get out and we can close this caper.", 
["addation_681bbc0132f84e05"] = "Teuer autos is our objective here. We\'re going to hit their dealership late in the evening. Should be quiet, not many civilians. They\'re a high-end joint. Deal in importing high-performance supercars from Europe and Japan. Those cars are a work of engineering beauty. And they\'re expensive - we\'re talking the price of a house in Georgetown here.", 
["addation_3e7e006276020ebe"] = "This one is a hit on the Teuer dealership. High class joint.", 
["addation_4b82725eb80fc223"] = "Outstanding work! These sweet motors will be in the hands of Arabian sheikhs within the week. Good job!", 
["addation_2835f25b659cede2"] = "OK, time to steal some cars.", 
["addation_313bb503a29b7399"] = "If you don\'t have a door, you make one. Time to use the blowtorch.", 
["addation_7db95f68c63db51a"] = "This car doesn\'t have a door, so you\'ll have to use a blowtorch to make one.", 
["addation_849820b42569433e"] = "The boxes are rigged with C4! Defuse them quick!", 
["addation_f61f10ab345ef801"] = "Don\'t just stand around! Get the gate open and secure the BCI tech.", 
["addation_7eb9f37445b1e678"] = "The tech is in our hands! Time to head back to the helicopter! Don\'t keep Bile waiting.", 
["addation_ecb61155c8660b02"] = "Good job. More cash is always welcome. Now, run back to the helicopter and get out of there.", 
["addation_eb7022f18221de8a"] = "One minute, gang! One minute.", 
["addation_714c242b7df81cf5"] = "Those oil barrels are blocking your path. Find the straps and release them. We don\'t have time to find another way.", 
["addation_a76d5b3481ff7d46"] = "You\'ll have to use the blowtorch to get through this gate. Make it quick.", 
["addation_9c02760c6680cde3"] = "You got a blowtorch, don\'t you? Use it on that gate.", 
["addation_5e6b0058d7016d94"] = "All safely down? Great. Locate the crash site, and see if the pilot\'s still alive. If he is, you need to get him to a safe place. I\'ll get a chopper out to pick him up ASAP. A plane doesn\'t crash out here without causing attention, so you can expect company. Work fast.", 
["addation_d6ef6c3a969fc002"] = "Great! Now that he\'s safe, I\'m sending a helicopter to pick him up. Stay with him.", 
["addation_d51bb94d81b801d4"] = "Chopper will come back for you, so while we\'re waiting, why not get looking for Vlad\'s packages. Could be a nice little bonus.", 
["addation_b3fd32f2ed331df5"] = "OK, chopper\'s pulling out. Hope you stowed some loot. It\'ll be back though. Try and find more of Vlad\'s coke.", 
["addation_a9921a79643d6976"] = "There goes the chopper, but don\'t worry - it\'ll be back. In the meantime, let\'s see if you can track down some more of those presents.", 
["addation_9fd418d61f5864f4"] = "Chopper\'s got to leave soon. Hustle if you want to be on it, but it\'ll be back soon!", 
["addation_e94186057227a18e"] = "Was that a coke-filled present falling from a tree? Christmas really is the time of miracles.", 
["addation_bede1f579b606bfb"] = "Do my ears deceive me, or was that the sweet sound of another of Vlad\'s presents hitting the floor? Look for it!", 
["addation_518caedb4cb63967"] = "The pilot just fell down. Damn, is he sleeping? You need to wake him up!", 
["addation_cd36c24bbaddde47"] = "Oh man, the pilot just went down again. Wake that old wino up!", 
["addation_fbb16596628eb6fe"] = "The chopper\'s coming to the lumber yard - be ready!", 
["addation_353344c387d3b2bc"] = "The helicopter is in bound for the lumber yard, gang.", 
["addation_a11da8ee09b1cdc5"] = "The chopper is coming at the antenna!", 
["addation_b204ef5e4d254e58"] = "Great, the pilot\'s safe! Place a flare on the table outside the yard. Ignite it to signal the helicopter.", 
["addation_c42e8dbe8e9c44c3"] = "Light another flare to bring the chopper back, gang.", 
["addation_9984819208f3ead8"] = "Alright, the chopper\'s on the way. He\'ll be there in a minute.", 
["addation_c121efc719f101db"] = "Good work. Just need to find one more keycard.", 
["addation_516851818deb80b7"] = "Great. Now get that other keycard working on the opposite gate. Hurry!", 
["addation_927de105a62f1d04"] = "Left gate activated. Now find another keycard, and let\'s get the other gate open.", 
["addation_a9684529a14f9c97"] = "Right panel\'s activated. Now get the other keycard, and let\'s get the second panel done.", 
["addation_bf8fd6c82b7d73e0"] = "You thought you were just going to stroll in through the main entrance? Look around for another way in.", 
["addation_c1a05a12c2a8b90f"] = "That\'s the guard dealt with. No need to worry about the cameras now.", 
["addation_e584ee102a4586b1"] = "This is the Left Control Room for the Dock Gate. Use the Keycard here.", 
["addation_8c1d2642b80bb844"] = "What are you waiting for? Into the docks.", 
["addation_b8dc5f77097a4a97"] = "This is the Storage Room. Check for a keycard. Might be a radio here too.", 
["addation_ef8941d3ceed9e15"] = "Ship\'s there. Get on it! Maybe deploy the zip-line - might speed things up.", 
["addation_f1fcd34407a242c4"] = "Moretta. This is Port Washington radio. Free to clear dock and berth at 3B. Stand by for GPS data. Over.", 
