["addation_3936ed315d908211"] = "No one\'ll see that there.", 
["addation_729e2ec5867ed26a"] = "You\'ve found the bomb. No need to keep checking the bomb cases!", 
["addation_459f1e9e797f4541"] = "Damn, no sign of the comm frequency. My guess is it\'ll be at the control room across the dock.", 
["addation_7d788c43d0c6ed3e"] = "Remember, you\'re looking for keycards. Check the buildings.", 
["addation_cc8cfc72c9590525"] = "You\'re looking for keycards. The buildings are your best bet.", 
["addation_59b218e9f646818d"] = "We need the Moretta\'s comm frequency. It\'ll be on one of those terminals. Get checking.", 
["addation_1e19435c0f4bb674"] = "Moretta\'s comm frequency will be on one of the computers. Check them out.", 
["addation_bc68092bdf48edb5"] = "We need the ship\'s comm frequency. Likely on one of these terminals. Search them!", 
["addation_8b8dce53675e57d7"] = "Moretta is moored at Dock 2B. Can\'t access it there.", 
["addation_29b3a95ee52a2c51"] = "Great job keeping it quiet. They don\'t suspect you, so the containers are unlocked. Have at it!", 
["addation_23b4c439a5d61e7c"] = "Plan B is en route, though. C4 can do the job loudly.", 
["addation_4cc63e99e5294551"] = "Third placed. One more.", 
["addation_4d709e390d80be65"] = "Boom! ", 
["addation_0dd2dbd999eb018a"] = "Just like St Nazaire! ", 
["addation_469d5a9b44070b20"] = "Well, we\'re not getting the Captain\'s cooperation now, but we still need that ship moved. Just hack the ship control terminal and make sure it stays on.", 
["addation_ca1437423829e2f3"] = "They cut the power. Get it back on.", 
["addation_e546571b48b56379"] = "Ship\'s there. Get on it!", 
["addation_e902b14a59d072cc"] = "What the? Ah fuuu... Containers were locked when the alarm tripped. Drill them!", 
["addation_d9fec16b828dbff7"] = "Keep the cops busy and the drill will be through in no time.", 
["addation_c4cde5cc3833bfa5"] = "And here\'s the second control room for the gate.", 
["addation_a83c6985f7700049"] = "Here\'s the second control room. Between the two, we can open the gate.", 
["addation_ee28fdd0cccdb040"] = "Guys! Use the keycard in the dock control room. Get the dock gate open.", 
["addation_dce913a72262573c"] = "You have to get off the gate before it will open. Health and safety bullshit!", 
["addation_7c3eddb9df9e0cce"] = "Come on, check those containers.", 
["addation_e85767249f3256d7"] = "Empty! Move on.", 
["addation_45c9c3305cea6047"] = "Wonder what\'s in the case. Could be The Butcher\'s explosives. Have a look.", 
["addation_41eb6baff2dcc910"] = "There\'s a boat ready for you. Head there.        ", 
["addation_bbb47ab0e10e57f9"] = "Still don\'t know you\'re there. Look for the keycards.", 
["addation_7a65362e0a99e8ca"] = "Still no sign of an alarm. Great. Find the comm frequency.", 
["addation_35883c2883f11acd"] = "You\'re keeping it quiet. Great. Now, the radio.", 
["addation_c9b3377c836c5e23"] = "All\'s quiet still. Good work. Stay hidden while the Moretta docks.", 
["addation_9a5b037e0dcca775"] = "Still no alarms. Now get on the ship.", 
