["addation_12f16809746c4bd0"] = "The C4 is for blowing the gate. Get it placed.", 
["addation_b435c2c1cf033720"] = "Away from the gate! Hustle it!", 
["addation_fa39af1cb9be4004"] = "Don\'t forget to turn the power back on. Blind here.", 
["addation_5115e8ff520160e6"] = "Almost got it... Almost got it.", 
["addation_4b4267939f04e54b"] = "Just a few... More... Seconds.", 
["addation_9220317b2efe78bb"] = "That manifest you picked up will point us to the right containers.", 
["addation_7de3c814a4d38308"] = "Gang, don\'t forget to crack those containers. Drill \'em!", 
["addation_8a4beb4f40b904fc"] = "Chopper\'s waiting for you. Hurry!", 
["addation_5435353d9312b9d1"] = "Boat\'s waiting for you. Get there!", 
["addation_20dacf1a3be3ddae"] = "Guys! Get to the boat!", 
["addation_074e067ed81169c2"] = "The boat won\'t escape the cops\' attention forever. Get there, now!", 
["addation_ca677e38dde922d3"] = "That looks like the cargo manifest. Good job! It narrows things down. This will make our job easier.", 
["addation_b7528bc4e89bff42"] = "Nice! We can shift that, make a little extra dollar.", 
["addation_1d714d22fa51f52f"] = "Get the Moretta out of the dock. When it\'s berth, get aboard, get the explosives, get out. Got it?", 
["addation_2236a1226113b6c6"] = "Vault\'s not here. OK, keep searching.", 
["addation_85308b79c19bb877"] = "Wasn\'t this one. Keep going. Vault is here somewhere.", 
["addation_0668a552c10b64c5"] = "Alright, now hook that hose to the vault.", 
["addation_266ef5b86f49463e"] = "Nice. Now get it back to the loot drop. ", 
["addation_5db23830df668835"] = "You\'re gonna need the thermite to pop the wagon open. Get back and grab it.", 
["addation_186287a327b48457"] = "Great! You can use this ladder to get up on the wagons.", 
["addation_861587d8c9a73464"] = "Guys, you need to find that wagon - the one with the vault.", 
["addation_4eb24bc1e2b2bf0a"] = "Keep looking for the wagon. Remember, we\'re looking for the one with the vault.", 
["addation_fff0ec94d2293478"] = "Good. Hose is OK. Let\'s get that pressure back. Start the pump.", 
["addation_78c685b501a2163b"] = "OK, we\'re pumping! Let it fill the vault.", 
["addation_f37f7df79dc21f6b"] = "Dammit! They yanked the hose. Get there, get it back on.", 
["addation_b6a747966df4e925"] = "Those wagons are bound for military decommissioning. One of \'em\'s gotta have C4.", 
["addation_133596b2af6a346a"] = "I know there\'s C4 in one of the wagons. Check \'em out!", 
["addation_55bfb7f0844540d8"] = "They set up a roadblock. And heavy reinforcements are on the way too.", 
["addation_457be54627de3983"] = "Got a plane en route to pick you up, but it can\'t land with trees blocking it\'s path. Find a saw, clear the trees and mark the landing with flares. Don\'t worry, CIA been doing this for years.", 
["addation_72c0c1629564a535"] = "Look at all this timber. There\'s got to be a saw somewhere - keep looking.", 
["addation_37e8b0c8c9b832fe"] = "Almost there. You should be able to hear it.", 
["addation_11168728836084c1"] = "We\'re almost there, gang. It\'s filling up nicely! Just keep things going a little more. Once it\'s full, we rig it and enjoy the show!", 
["addation_990aba2127efc489"] = "Keep the water flowing, gang. Just a little more. Then just rig it, and let hydrodynamics do its job.", 
["addation_b94777af846f0bcd"] = "All that wagon is waiting for is a nice bit of C4. Get to it!", 
["addation_cd1ae456f52d1225"] = "There\'ll be a couple of keycards out there, maybe in the trunks of cars. They\'ll help you get silent access to the vault. Or you can forget that Mission Impossible crap and unleash Ragnarok. Up to you.", 
["addation_cf652616b6570f93"] = "Two ways to go about this, gentlemen. Go loud - you know how to do that. But if you\'re hoping to raise your game, look for two keycards and unlock the vault. Car trunks are a good place to look.", 
["addation_69263cfbae12c39e"] = "You got one of the keycards, now find the other one.", 
["addation_a8733f2977cf53fb"] = "Great. Now just wait for that time lock to run down. So far this is textbook stuff. Be ready to bag the cash when it opens.", 
["addation_f8af584d218696c0"] = "There we go! Vault is open. Get to work on bagging that cash! ", 
["addation_a0b0d9267ae656e3"] = "Piles of green! Thats why we\'re in this business, gang. ", 
["addation_5888ac32d6bc959d"] = "That\'s the cash. Remember, unless you want the cops there, get a bag over the yellow wall. Don\'t worry - that blackmailing asswipe will get what\'s coming to him.", 
["addation_754472a1dfeacb3b"] = "Keep the people down. Keep them quiet.", 
["addation_ad7827e1ad195bb2"] = "We need that vault open. Quiet with keycards, or bust it open with a drill.", 
["addation_708dbf7e9ac50e73"] = "That\'s one card entered, but the vault needs two. Keep looking.", 
["addation_2b355de55f210af1"] = "Your driver had to bail. He left behind a drill. Get it, and use it on the vault.", 
["addation_25bde8d4634feacd"] = "Uh... Yeah... Their radios aren\'t working. Sunspot activity.", 
["addation_b4d126355e81233a"] = "Goddammit, a laser gate. We\'ve dealt with these before. Just wait for it to flicker off, and then dash through.", 
["addation_0e642e36bc9f4cb4"] = "Thats it! Now let\'s get it to work on that vault.", 
["addation_4a0eea653cc50273"] = "This is Roberts Bank. How may I help you today?", 
["addation_529e410355763ab2"] = "It would give me a lot of pleasure to assist you.", 
["addation_b378743b4960a0ad"] = "He\'s almost there. Watch where he drops the bags. Grab them, assemble the cage, and send up the balloon. You\'re going to like this.", 
["addation_d11de4d1b8d5ffb0"] = "Drills done! Vault\'s opening! Go for the cash!", 
["addation_d36e84df881a9959"] = "Carry the bags to the parking lot. Get the cage put together there. ", 
["addation_3b98edda2f2f0c02"] = "That\'s perfect. The cage is assembled.", 
["addation_f1ed012fc5a65a68"] = "When you have enough bags, let the balloon go, and stand back.", 
["addation_5df14b14f550c2f8"] = "Dammit! The plane missed the cable. Alright. Still time for another pass. Stand by.", 
["addation_3b7384c72cd825e4"] = "That\'s your way out, but you can\'t leave yet. Wipe the crap off your shoes and secure the money.", 
["addation_f53f401996170f2b"] = "Plane is en route. Just hold on, gang.", 
["addation_55e7650379b4dcb2"] = "Well, so much for stealth. But the job\'s half done. Just get that money out of there.", 
["addation_102f4956e919c6b3"] = "No more stealthing it, crew. But finish the job. Get that cash out of the vault.", 
["addation_f42f069c4690e7dc"] = "The alarm. But no matter. We got enough cash. ", 
["addation_c703973eb3b094fe"] = "This isn\'t a request. Get your ass into position for a roof pick-up, or I\'ll see whole squadrons of F-16\'s scrambled in your direction!", 
["addation_30eef0412700ef3c"] = "Plane is coming in hot. He\'ll collect from the roof. Make sure everything is ready.", 
["addation_2c3bf7ddd60690a3"] = "The pick-up is on its way. Not much margin for error here. Get to the roof.", 
["addation_80d004ee1897ab69"] = "The plane will be picking up the cage from the street. Get it ready.", 
["addation_d3aaa3a0f81de36e"] = "The parking lot is the pilots target for the pick-up. Get there, get everything ready.", 
["addation_6deec1ce92476d57"] = "Look around. The codes must be written somewhere. I can\'t stall them forever!", 
["addation_f89be5a2c3918e06"] = "Today\'s code is 559732. Sorry it took so long.", 
