["addation_4a1708703a20cdac"] = "Alright, the alarm is dead. Good job. You can come and go as you like.", 
["addation_3c64ede929887a74"] = "Our target will be in the panic room. Look for it. Once you\'ve found it, we can work on winkling that traitor bastard out.", 
["addation_dd9c9eefb1b7159e"] = "Damn. The panic room has more reinforcment than I expected. State Department didnt cut corners. We\'re gonna need a thermal lance. I\'ll call in Bile.", 
