["addation_6dbc541dc4621315"] = "We\'re at the night club. Time to get your dance-on. Start by "casing" the place before the fun begins. Take a look around first and keep things casual.", 
["addation_a30f1655a4780a51"] = "I\'m getting a helicopter to pick you up, but it\'s gonna take some time.", 
