["addation_1142e17cd1653be6"] = "Get inside the store and take the clerk hostage, so we can make a trade with the cops.", 
["addation_3503026adbb12e19"] = "Head for the store and grab a hostage so we can negotiate our friend back from the cops.", 
["addation_6cfdf5c9127dc109"] = "You take it easy for now, while I make a deal with the cops.", 
["addation_948d8d72c98f9c87"] = "OK, it\'s done. Release the hostage now to trade back our friend.", 
["addation_21f75d3895a5d2c5"] = "Time to go. No time for lock-picking, just shoot off the door handle.", 
