["addation_38ba32f6e8394ab2"] = "Doors. You can try these out too. Keep in mind that there are lots of ways to get one open. In our line of work, closing doors is pointless - opening \'em is what matters.", 
["addation_f344d6fa7bd59557"] = "So the safes can be drilled, even picked - if you have the skill.", 
["addation_e848b6d65d8417b0"] = "I know this is elementary for you, but practice is practice, right?", 
["addation_744e3212d9136086"] = "Cameras. Everybody hates cameras. I set up a room with a couple variations for you to test your stealth. No shame in failure and also no one shooting at you, which is nice.", 
